erience difficulties setting up or using two-factor authentication. Instead, using the "Optional" mode for users with the customer role is recommended which will allow customers to enable 2FA, but will not require them to do so.'=>'不建议要求客户使用 2FA，因为有些客户在设置或使用双因素身份验证时可能会遇到困难。建议对具有客户角色的用户使用「可选」模式，这将允许客户启用 2FA，但不会要求他们这样做。','Wordfence 2FA'=>'Wordfence 2FA','<html><body><p>You do not currently have two-factor authentication active on your account, which will be required beginning %s.</p><p><a href="%s">Configure 2FA</a></p></body></html>'=>'<html><body><p>您的账户目前没有启用双因素身份验证，在 %s 开始时需要启用。</p><p><a href="%s">配置 2FA</a></p></body></html>','The specified URL is invalid.'=>'指定的 URL 无效。','Are you sure you want to delete the selected Wordfence data? If you reactivate Wordfence later, deleted settings and history cannot be recovered.'=>'您确定要删除选择 Wordfence 数据吗？如果您以后重新激活 Wordfence，删除的设置和历史记录将无法恢复。','Delete Wordfence Data?'=>'删除 Wordfence 数据？','The Wordfence firewall is still optimized. You should remove the firewall\'s extended protection before deleting to avoid PHP errors if some firewall files cannot be removed, or if PHP\'s "auto_prepend_file" setting is cached.'=>'Wordfence 防火墙仍在优化中。如果某些防火墙文件无法删除，或者 PHP 的「auto_prepend_file」设置被缓存，您应该在删除前移除防火墙的扩展保护，以避免 PHP 出错。','Extended Protection Still Enabled'=>'仍启用扩展保护','Deactivate and Delete Data'=>'停用并删除数据','Deactivate Wordfence'=>'停用 Wordfence','Invalid option specified'=>'指定的选项无效','Delete Login Security tables and 2FA codes, but keep Wordfence tables and data'=>'删除登录安全表和 2FA 代码，但保留 Wordfence 表和数据','Delete Wordfence tables and data, but keep Login Security tables and 2FA codes'=>'删除 Wordfence 表和数据，但保留登录安全表和 2FA 代码','Keep all Wordfence tables and data'=>'保留所有 Wordfence 表和数据','Please try again. If the problem persists, please <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/help/api-key" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">contact Wordfence Support<span class="screen-reader-text">(opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'请重试。如果问题仍然存在，请<a href="https://www.wordfence.com/help/api-key" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">联系 Wordfence 支持 <span class="screen-reader-text">（在新标签页打开）</span></a>','An error occurred while installing your license key.'=>'安装许可证密钥时发生错误。','Congratulations! Wordfence Free is now active on your website.'=>'恭喜您！Wordfence 免费版已在您的网站上激活。','Congratulations! Wordfence Care is now active on your website. Please note that some Care features are not enabled by default.'=>'恭喜！Wordfence Care 已在您的网站上激活。请注意，某些 Care 功能默认情况下并未启用。','Care License Installed'=>'已安装 Care 许可证','Congratulations! Wordfence Response is now active on your website. Please note that some Response features are not enabled by default.'=>'恭喜！Wordfence 响应已在您的网站上激活。请注意，某些响应功能默认未启用。','Response License Installed'=>'已安装响应许可证','Get a new license'=>'获取新许可证','This is where future security alerts for your website will be sent. This can also be changed in Global Options.'=>'这是您网站未来安全警报的发送位置。这也可以在「全局选项」中更改。','Please enter a valid email address'=>'请输入有效的邮箱地址','Email'=>'邮箱','Install an existing license'=>'安装现有许可证','Get Your Wordfence License'=>'获取 Wordfence 许可证','Register with Wordfence to secure your site with the latest threat intelligence.'=>'注册 Wordfence，使用最新的威胁情报保护您的网站。','Install your license to finish activating Wordfence.'=>'安装许可证以完成激活 Wordfence。','You must install a license to continue using Wordfence.'=>'您必须安装许可证才能继续使用 Wordfence。','An unexpected error occurred while attempting to dismiss the notice. Please try again.'=>'在尝试删除通知时发生了意外错误。请重试。','You will be reminded again in 12 hours.'=>'我们将在 12 小时后再次提醒您。','Notice Dismissed'=>'撤销通知','Remind Me Later'=>'稍后提醒我','An unexpected error occurred while attempting to configure Wordfence to delete its data on deactivation.'=>'在尝试配置 Wordfence 删除停用时的数据时发生了意外错误。','You are about to deactivate Wordfence. Would you like to delete its data or keep it in place?'=>'您即将停用 Wordfence。您想删除数据还是保留数据？','Delete all Wordfence tables and data'=>'删除所有 Wordfence 表和数据','This could be caused by a database problem. You may need to repair your "wfconfig" database table or fix your database user\'s privileges if they have changed recently, or you may need to reinstall Wordfence. Please <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">contact Wordfence support<span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'这可能是数据库问题造成的。您可能需要修复您的「wfconfig」数据库表，或者如果您的数据库用户权限最近发生了变化，您可能需要修复数据库用户权限，或者您可能需要重新安装 Wordfence。请 <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">联系 Wordfence 支持<span class="screen-reader-text"> (','Wordfence\'s license key is missing.'=>'Wordfence 的许可证密钥丢失。','An unknown error occurred.'=>'发生未知错误。','Install Wordfence'=>'安装 Wordfence','An error occurred while retrieving your license information from the Wordfence servers. Please ensure that your server can reach www.wordfence.com on port 443.'=>'从 Wordfence 服务器检索许可证信息时发生错误。请确保您的服务器可以通过 443 端口访问 www.wordfence.com。','The link you used to access this page has expired, has already been used, or is otherwise invalid.'=>'您用于访问此页面的链接已过期、已被使用或无效。','Too many installation requests have been made from your IP address. Please try again later.'=>'从您的 IP 地址进行的安装要求过多。请稍后再试。','Wordfence is already installed on this site. If you need to replace the current license, you may do so by visiting the "All Options" page of the Wordfence menu.'=>'本网站已安装 Wordfence。如果您需要更换当前许可证，请访问 Wordfence 菜单的「所有选项」页面。','If this option is disabled, Wordfence can look up countries for visitor IP addresses using a local database, but cannot look up regions or cities'=>'如果禁用此选项，Wordfence 可以使用本地数据库查询访问者 IP 地址所在的国家，但不能查询地区或城市。','Scan Stage Failed'=>'扫描阶段失败','Wordfence will make up to %d attempts to resume each failed scan stage. This scan may recover if one of these attempts is successful.'=>'Wordfence 最多会尝试 %d 来恢复每个失败的扫描阶段。如果其中一次尝试成功，扫描可能会恢复。','Wordfence will make one attempt to resume each failed scan stage. This scan may recover if this attempt is successful.'=>'Wordfence 将尝试恢复每个失败的扫描阶段。如果尝试成功，此扫描可能会恢复。','Attempting to resume scan stage (%d attempt(s) remaining)...'=>'尝试恢复扫描阶段（剩余 %d 次尝试）...','Cached result for scan start test: %s'=>'扫描开始测试的缓存结果：%s','To protect your site from this vulnerability, the safest option is to deactivate and completely remove "%s" until a patched version is available. <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Get more information.<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'要保护您的网站免受此漏洞的攻击，最安全的选项是完全删除「%s」，直到有修补版本为止。<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">获取更多信息。 <span class="screen-reader-text">（在新标签页打开）</span></a>','The Plugin "%s" has a security vulnerability.'=>'「%s」插件存在安全漏洞。','Connecting back to this site via IPv6 (not required; failure to connect may not be an issue on some sites) <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="wfhelp"><span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'通过 IPv6 连接回本网站（不是必需的；在某些网站上连接失败可能不是问题）<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="wfhelp"><span class="screen-reader-text">（在新标签页打开）</span></a>','Invalid number of scan resume attempts specified: %d'=>'指定的扫描恢复尝试次数无效：%d','This page shows information that can be used for troubleshooting conflicts, configuration issues, or compatibility with other plugins, themes, or a host\'s environment. Failing tests are not always a sign of something that you need to fix, but can help the Wordfence team when troubleshooting a problem. (<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Learn More <span class="screen-reader-text">opens in new tab</span></a>)'=>'该页面显示的信息可用于排除与其他插件、主题或主机环境的冲突、配置问题或兼容性。测试失败并不总是您需要修复的问题，但可以帮助 Wordfence 团队排除故障。(<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">了解更多<span class="screen-reader-text">在新标签页打开</span></a>)','Maximum number of attempts to resume each scan stage'=>'恢复每个扫描阶段的最大尝试次数','Look up visitor IP locations via Wordfence servers'=>'通过 Wordfence 服务器查询访客 IP 位置','This option requires cURL. (This may have no effect on some old PHP or cURL versions.)'=>'此选项需要 cURL。(这可能对某些旧的 PHP 或 cURL 版本没有影响）。','Use only IPv4 to start scans'=>'仅使用 IPv4 启动扫描','UA/Hostname/Referrer/IP Range not allowed'=>'不允许 UA/ 主机名 / 引用程序 /IP 范围','Automatic updates enabled'=>'启用自动更新','Automatic updates disabled'=>'禁用自动更新','Disables automatic updates'=>'禁用自动更新','Cron is enabled'=>'启用 Cron','Cron is disabled'=>'禁用 Cron','This diagnostic requires cURL'=>'此诊断需要 cURL','This diagnostic is unavailable as cURL appears to be supported, but was not used by WordPress for this request'=>'此诊断不可用，因为 cURL 似乎是受支持的，但 WordPress 在此要求中并未使用。','This likely indicates that the server either does not support IPv6 or does not have an IPv6 address assigned or associated with the domain. Original error message: %s'=>'这可能表明服务器不支持 IPv6 或没有 IPv6 地址指派或与域名无关。原始错误信息：%s','IPv6 DNS resolution failed'=>'IPv6 DNS 解析失败','When enabled, the last login timestamp will be displayed for each user on the WP Users page. When used in conjunction with reCAPTCHA, the most recent score will also be displayed for each user.'=>'启用后，WP 用户页面上每个用户的最后登录时间戳将显示。与 reCAPTCHA 结合使用时，每个用户的最新得分也将显示。','Show last login column on WP Users page'=>'在 WP 用户页面上显示最后登录列','Allowlisted IP addresses that bypass 2FA and reCAPTCHA'=>'允许列出绕过 2FA 和 reCAPTCHA 的 IP 地址','Login Security: Allowlisted IP addresses that bypass 2FA and reCAPTCHA'=>'登录安全：允许绕过 2FA 和验证码的 IP 地址列表','Ignoring invalid scan file child: %s'=>'忽略无效扫描文件 child: %s','Ignoring invalid base scan file: %s'=>'忽略无效基础扫描文件: %s','Ignoring invalid expected scan file: %s'=>'忽略无效预期扫描文件: %s','Ignoring invalid scan path: %s'=>'忽略无效扫描路径: %s','This was a premium license key, but it is no longer valid, so premium features are disabled. You can either remove the invalid key and continue using Wordfence\'s free features, or enter a new premium key to upgrade. If you have questions, contact <a href="mailto:billing@wordfence.com">billing@wordfence.com</a>.'=>'这是高级许可证密钥，但已失效，因此高级功能被禁用。您可以删除无效密钥并继续使用 Wordfence 的免费功能，或者输入新的高级密钥进行升级。如有问题，请联系 <a href="mailto:billing@wordfence.com">billing@wordfence.com</a> 。','Remove Invalid License'=>'删除无效许可证','Premium License Deactivated'=>'高级许可证已停用','Unable to read file contents'=>'无法读取文件内容','Empty file path provided'=>'空文件路径提供','This link has expired. Refresh the scan results page and try again.'=>'此链接已过期。刷新扫描结果页面并重试。','Edit Wordfence Options'=>'编辑 Wordfence 选项','The site admin can change this option.'=>'网站管理员可以更改此选项。','Application Passwords'=>'应用程序密码','Wordfence Firewall &amp; Care License Enabled'=>'已启用 Wordfence 防火墙和维护许可证','Wordfence Firewall &amp; Response License Enabled'=>'已启用 Wordfence 防火墙和响应许可证','Sign up for Wordfence Care and we’ll take care of it. Our security experts will clean your site, resolve the infection, and perform a security audit. Get hands-on support with any security issue including help installing, configuring and optimizing Wordfence.'=>'注册 Wordfence Care，我们将为您提供服务。我们的安全专家将清理您的网站，解决感染问题，并执行安全审计。获得任何安全问题的实际支持，包括帮助安装、配置和优化 Wordfence。','Need help with a security issue?'=>'需要安全问题帮助？','Learn More About Wordfence Response'=>'了解有关 Wordfence 响应的更多信息','Learn More About Wordfence Care'=>'了解有关 Wordfence 关怀的更多信息','Sign up for Wordfence Care today and get expert help with any security issue. Wordfence Care is for business owners who put a premium on their time. With Wordfence Care, we take care of it, so that you can focus on your customers. Check out Wordfence Response for mission-critical WordPress websites.'=>'立即注册 Wordfence Care，获得专家帮助，解决任何安全问题。Wordfence Care 专为时间宝贵的企业主而设。有了 Wordfence Care，我们可以帮您解决这些问题，让您可以专注于您的客户。查看 Wordfence Response，了解适用于任务关键型 WordPress 网站的服务。','Wordfence Scan &amp; Care License Enabled'=>'已启用 Wordfence 扫描与防护许可','Wordfence Scan &amp; Response License Enabled'=>'启用 Wordfence 扫描和响应许可证','We have updated our policies. To continue using Wordfence, you will need to read and agree to the Wordfence License Terms and Conditions, the Services Subscription Agreement, and Terms of Service, and read and acknowledge the Wordfence Privacy Policy by clicking Review.'=>'我们已经更新了我们的政策。要继续使用 Wordfence，您需要阅读并同意 Wordfence 许可条款和条件、服务订购协议和服务条款，并通过点击「查看」阅读并确认 Wordfence 隐私政策。','We have updated our policies. To continue using Wordfence, you will need to read and agree to the <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/license-terms-and-conditions/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Wordfence License Terms and Conditions<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>, the <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/services-subscription-agreement" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Services Subscription Agreement<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>, and <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/terms-of-service/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Terms of Service<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>, and read and acknowledge the <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/privacy-policy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Wordfence Privacy Policy<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>.'=>'我们更新了我们的政策。要继续使用 Wordfence，您需要阅读并同意 <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/license-terms-and-conditions/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Wordfence 许可条款和条件 <span class="screen-reader-text">(在新标签页打开)</span></a>、<a href="https://www.wordfence.com/services-subscription-agreement" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">服务订阅协议 <span class="screen-reader-text">(在新标签页打开)</span></a>和<a href="https://www.wordfence.com/terms-of-service/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">服务条款 <span class="screen-reader-text">(在新标签页打开)</span></a>，并阅读和确认 <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/privacy-policy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Wordfence 隐私政策 <span class="screen-reader-text">(在新标签页打开)</span></a>。','<p>Are you sure you want to reset this site\'s Wordfence License? This will disable Premium features and return the site to the free version of Wordfence. Your settings will still be retained when reinstalling a license.</p><p>If autorenew is enabled for the current license, the license will renew at the next expiration date. If you would like to turn renewal off or assign the license to another site, log into wordfence.com to change it.</p>'=>'<p>您确定要重置本网站的 Wordfence 许可证吗？这将禁用高级功能，使网站返回到免费版 Wordfence。重新安装许可证时，您的设置仍将保留。</p><p>如果当前许可证启用了自动续期，许可证将在下一个到期日续期。如果您想关闭更新或将许可证分配给其他网站，请登录 wordfence.com 进行更改。</p>','Confirm Reset'=>'确认重置','Click here to manage your Wordfence licenses'=>'单击此处管理您的 Wordfence 许可证','Reset site to a free license'=>'重置网站为免费许可证','%s License Active'=>'%s 许可证激活','%s License Expired'=>'%s 许可证已过期','Upgrade to Response'=>'升级到响应','Upgrade to Care'=>'升级到关怀','Free'=>'免费','Wordfence Free'=>'免费版','Wordfence Premium'=>'高级版','Wordfence Response'=>'Wordfence 响应','Care'=>'关怀','Wordfence Care'=>'Wordfence 关怀','Upgrade to a 24/7 1-hour response time with Wordfence Response'=>'通过 Wordfence 响应服务升级到全天候 1 小时响应时间','Upgrade to hands-on support with Wordfence Care'=>'通过 Wordfence 关怀升级到实践支持','As a Wordfence Premium customer you\'re entitled to paid support via our ticketing system. Our senior support engineers respond to Premium tickets during regular business hours (Monday to Friday, 6am to 5pm Pacific and 9am to 8pm Eastern time) and have a direct line to our QA and development teams.'=>'作为 Wordfence 高级客户，您有权通过我们的票务系统获得付费支持。我们的高级支持工程师会在正常工作时间（周一至周五，太平洋时间早 6 点至晚 5 点，东部时间早 9 点至晚 8 点）回复高级支持票单，并可直接联系我们的质量保证和开发团队。','As a Wordfence Care customer you are entitled to hands-on priority support and have access to our incident response team. Our senior support engineers and incident response team respond to requests quickly within business hours (Monday to Friday, 6am to 5pm Pacific and 9am to 8pm Eastern time) and can sign-in to your site on request to assist with complex issues.'=>'作为 Wordfence Care 客户，您有权获得优先支持并与我们的事件响应团队联系。我们的高级支持工程师和事件响应团队会在工作时间内（周一至周五，太平洋时间上午 6 点至下午 5 点，东部时间上午 9 点至晚上 8 点）快速响应请求，并可根据请求登录您的网站，协助解决综合问题。','As a Wordfence Response customer you are entitled to hands-on priority support 24 hours a day 365 days a year. Our incident response team is available out of hours to handle urgent issues and security incidents. Our customer support team is available during business hours (Monday to Friday, 6am to 5pm Pacific and 9am to 8pm Eastern time) for product assistance. Both teams can sign-in to your site to assist, on request.'=>'作为 Wordfence 响应客户，您有权获得全年 365 天、每天 24 小时的优先支持。我们的事件响应团队可在非工作时间处理紧急问题和安全事件。我们的客户支持团队可在工作时间（周一至周五，太平洋时间上午 6 点至下午 5 点，东部时间上午 9 点至晚上 8 点）提供产品帮助。两个团队都可以应要求登录您的网站提供帮助。','Learn about Wordfence Response'=>'了解 Wordfence 响应','Learn about Wordfence Care and Wordfence Response'=>'了解 Wordfence Care 和 Wordfence 响应','%s Enabled'=>'%s 已启用','Automatic uninstallation cannot be completed, but you may still be able to <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">manually uninstall extended protection<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>.'=>'自动卸载无法完成，但您仍然可以<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">手动卸载扩展保护 <span class="screen-reader-text">（在新标签页打开）</span></a>。','If you cannot complete the uninstall process, <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%s">click here for help<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'如果无法完成卸载过程，<a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%s">单击此处获取帮助 <span class="screen-reader-text">（在新标签页打开）</span></a>。','If you don\'t recognize this file, please <a href="https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/wordfence" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">contact us on the WordPress support forums<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a> before proceeding.'=>'如果您无法识别该文件，请<a href="https://wordpress.org/support/plugin/wordfence" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">在继续操作前通过 WordPress 支持论坛 <span class="screen-reader-text">（在新标签页打开）</span></a>联系我们。','You can find more details on alternative setup steps, including installation on SiteGround or for multiple sites sharing a single php.ini, <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%s">in our documentation<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>.'=>'您可以在我们的文档<a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%s"><span class="screen-reader-text">（在新标签页打开）</span></a>中找到有关其他设置步骤的更多详情，包括在 SiteGround 上安装或多个网站共享一个 php.ini。','The Web Application Firewall is currently in Learning Mode. <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Learn More<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'Web 应用程序防火墙当前处于学习模式。<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">了解更多 <span class="screen-reader-text">（在新标签页打开）</span></a>。','You can log in to <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">wordfence.com<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a> to accept the updated terms and privacy policy for all of your license keys at once.'=>'您可以登录 <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">wordfence.com<span class="screen-reader-text">（在新标签页打开）</span></a>一次性接受所有许可证密钥的更新条款和隐私政策。','For most sites, we recommend allowing access from the United States, where Google and other benign crawlers are located. Some well-known crawlers also have locations in Europe, so be careful when blocking other countries, especially if you have not seen significant attacks from them.'=>'对于大多数网站，我们建议允许从谷歌和其他良性爬虫所在的美国进行访问。一些知名的爬虫也在欧洲设有分支机构，因此在屏蔽其他国家时要小心谨慎，尤其是在您没有看到来自这些国家的重大攻击时。','U.S. Blocked'=>'屏蔽美国','Error Saving Block'=>'错误保存阻止','If you use Google Ads, blocking countries from accessing the entire site is not recommended. <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Learn More<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'如果您使用 Google Ads，不建议从整个网站访问时屏蔽国家 / 地区。<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">了解更多 <span class="screen-reader-text">（在新标签中打开）</span></a>','Allow a grace period for this user prior to requiring Wordfence 2FA'=>'在要求使用 Wordfence 2FA 之前，允许该用户有一个宽限期','2FA Grace Period'=>'2FA 宽限期','View users'=>'查看用户','When enabled, reCAPTCHA and 2FA prompt support will be added to WooCommerce login and registration forms in addition to the default WordPress forms. Testing WooCommerce forms after enabling this feature is recommended to ensure plugin compatibility.'=>'启用后，除了默认的 WordPress 表单外，WooCommerce 登录和注册表单也将添加 reCAPTCHA 和 2FA 提示支持。建议在启用此功能后测试 WooCommerce 表单，以确保插件的兼容性。','Page '=>'页面','N/A'=>'不适用','Page %d is out of range'=>'页面 %d 超出范围','No users found in the %s state for the %s role'=>'在 %s 状态下未找到 %s 角色的用户','2FA is not required for the %s role'=>'%s 角色不需要 2FA','This page only shows users and roles on the main site of this network'=>'本页面只显示本网络主网站上的用户和角色','Send Anyway'=>'无论如何发送','Notify'=>'通知','For roles that require 2FA, users will have this many days to set up 2FA. Failure to set up 2FA during this period will result in the user losing account access. This grace period will apply to new users from the time of account creation. For existing users, this grace period will apply relative to the time at which the requirement is implemented. This grace period will not automatically apply to admins and must be manually enabled for each admin user.'=>'对于需要 2FA 的角色，用户将有这么多天的时间来设置 2FA。如果在此期间未设置 2FA，用户将失去账户访问权限。该宽限期适用于新用户，从账户创建时开始计算。对于现有用户，该宽限期适用于实施该要求的时间。宽限期不会自动应用于管理员，必须为每个管理员用户手动启用。','Setting the grace period to 0 will prevent users in roles where 2FA is required, including newly created users, from logging in if they have not already enabled two-factor authentication.'=>'如果将宽限期设置为 0，则需要 2FA 的角色中的用户（包括新创建的用户）尚未启用双因素身份验证时，将无法启用日志。','2FA Roles'=>'2FA 角色','An error was encountered while trying to disable NTP. Please try again.'=>'在尝试登录 NTP 时遇到错误。请重试。','Error Disabling NTP'=>'错误禁用 NTP','An error was encountered while trying to reset the NTP state. Please try again.'=>'在尝试重置 NTP 状态时遇到错误。请重试。','Error Resetting NTP'=>'重置 NTP 时出错','NTP will be automatically disabled after 1 more attempt.'=>'再尝试一次后，NTP 将自动禁用。','NTP will be automatically disabled after %d more attempts.'=>'再尝试 %d 次后，NTP 将自动禁用。','NTP updates are currently failing.'=>'当前 NTP 更新失败。','NTP is currently <strong>enabled</strong>.'=>'NTP 当前<strong>启用</strong>。','Reset'=>'重置','NTP was manually disabled.'=>'NTP 已被手动禁用。','NTP is currently disabled as %d subsequent attempts have failed.'=>'由于 %d 次尝试失败，NTP 当前已禁用。','The constant WORDFENCE_LS_DISABLE_NTP is defined which disables NTP entirely. Remove this constant or set it to a falsy value to enable NTP.'=>'常量 WORDFENCE_LS_DISABLE_NTP 被定义为完全禁用 NTP。删除该常量或将其设置为假值，即可启用 NTP。','NTP is a protocol that allows for remote time synchronization. Wordfence Login Security uses this protocol to ensure that it has the most accurate time which is necessary for TOTP-based two-factor authentication.'=>'NTP 是一种允许远程同步时间的协议。Wordfence 登录安全软件使用此协议来确保它拥有最准确的时间，这对于基于 TOTP 的双因素身份验证是必要的。','Note: This feature requires a free site key and secret for the <a href="https://www.google.com/recaptcha/about/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google reCAPTCHA v3 Service</a>. To set up new reCAPTCHA keys, log into your Google account and go to the <a href="https://www.google.com/recaptcha/admin" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">reCAPTCHA admin page</a>.'=>'注意：该功能需要 <a href="https://www.google.com/recaptcha/about/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google reCAPTCHA v3 Service</a> 的免费密钥和秘密。要设置新的验证码密钥，请登录您的谷歌账户并访问 <a href="https://www.google.com/recaptcha/admin" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">reCAPTCHA 管理页面</a>。','Two-factor authentication will be required for user <strong>%s</strong> beginning <strong>%s</strong>.'=>'用户<strong>%s</strong> 开始<strong>%s</strong> 时需要双因素验证。','Two-factor authentication will be required for your account beginning <strong>%s</strong>'=>'从<strong>%s</strong> 开始，您的账户需要双因素身份验证。','An unexpected error occurred while attempting to revoke the grace period.'=>'在尝试撤销宽限期时发生了意外错误。','Revoke Grace Period'=>'撤销宽限期','Unable to Revoke Grace Period'=>'无法撤销宽限期','An unexpected error occurred while attempting to reset the grace period.'=>'尝试撤销宽限期时发生意外错误。','An unexpected error occurred while attempting to activate the grace period.'=>'尝试激活宽限期时发生意外错误。','Reset Grace Period'=>'重置宽限期','Activate Grace Period'=>'激活宽限期','days'=>'天数','Grace Period Override'=>'覆盖宽限期','Unable to Reset Grace Period'=>'无法重置宽限期','Unable to Activate Grace Period'=>'无法激活宽限期','Users without 2FA active (%s)'=>'无 2FA 的用户已启用 (%s)','Grace Period'=>'宽限期','<strong>LOGIN BLOCKED</strong>: 2FA is required to be active on your account. Please contact the site administrator.'=>'<strong>登录受阻</strong>: 您的帐户需要启用 2FA。请联系网站管理员。','Two-factor authentication must be activated for this account prior to %s.'=>'此帐户必须在 %s 之前启用双因素身份验证。','Two-factor authentication must be activated for your account prior to %s to avoid losing access.'=>'您的帐户必须在 %s 之前启用双因素身份验证，以免失去访问权。','Two-factor authentication is required for this account, but has not been configured.'=>'此帐户需要双因素身份验证，但尚未配置。','Two-factor authentication is required for your account, but has not been configured.'=>'您的帐户需要双因素身份验证，但尚未配置。','Manage Settings'=>'管理设置','WooCommerce appears to be installed, but the Wordfence Login Security WooCommerce integration is not currently enabled. Without this feature, WooCommerce forms will not support all functionality provided by Wordfence Login Security, including CAPTCHA for the login page and user registration.'=>'WooCommerce 似乎已安装，但 Wordfence 登录安全 WooCommerce 集成目前尚未启用。如果没有该功能，WooCommerce 表单将不支持 Wordfence 登录安全提供的所有功能，包括登录页面和用户注册的验证码。','Locked Out<small class="wfls-sub-status">(Grace Period Exceeded)</small>'=>'锁定 <small class="wfls-sub-status">（超过宽限期）</small>','Locked Out<small class="wfls-sub-status">(Grace Period Disabled)</small>'=>'锁定 <small class="wfls-sub-status">（宽限期已禁用）</small>','Inactive<small class="wfls-sub-status">(Grace Period)</small>'=>'不活动 <small class="wfls-sub-status">（宽限期）</small>','Unable to dismiss notice'=>'无法解除通知','Failed to reset grace period'=>'未能重置宽限期','Invalid grace period override'=>'无效的宽限期覆盖','Invalid user specified'=>'指定的无效用户','All users with the selected role already have two-factor authentication activated or have been locked out.'=>'所有具有选择角色的用户都已激活双因素身份验证或已被锁定。','No users currently exist with the selected role.'=>'目前不存在具有选择角色的用户。','More than %d users exist for the selected role. This notification is not designed to handle large groups of users. In such instances, using a different solution for notifying users of upcoming 2FA requirements is recommended.'=>'选择角色的用户超过 %d。该通知不是为处理大群用户而设计的。在这种情况下，建议使用其他解决方案通知用户即将到来的 2FA 要求。','You do not have permission to dismiss this notice.'=>'您没有权利限制驳回本通知。','You do not have permission to disable NTP.'=>'您没有权利限制撤销 NTP。','You do not have permission to reset the NTP failure count.'=>'您没有权限限制重置 NTP 故障计数。','You do not have permission to revoke the 2FA grace period.'=>'您没有权限撤销 2FA 宽限期。','You do not have permission to reset the 2FA grace period.'=>'您没有权限重置 2FA 宽限期。','Enable %d scan option.'=>'启用 %d 扫描选项。','Re-enable %d firewall rule.'=>'重新启用 %d 防火墙规则。','Regex compilation failed for signature %d'=>'签名 %d 的 Regex 编译失败','<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Learn More<span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">了解更多 <span class="screen-reader-text">(','If you cannot complete the setup process, <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%s">click here for help<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>.'=>'如果您无法完成设置过程，<a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%s">点击此处获取帮助 <span class="screen-reader-text">（在新的分页中打开）</span></a>。','Wordfence country blocking is currently set to block the United States. We recommend allowing access from the United States for Google and other benign crawlers, unless you choose to only block the login page.'=>'Wordfence 国家拦截目前设置为拦截美国。我们建议允许谷歌和其他良性爬虫从美国访问，除非您选择只阻止登录页面。','<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Get more information.<span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">获取更多信息。 <span class="screen-reader-text">(','<a href="%1$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">%1$s<span class="scr