ank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="wf-help-link">Learn more<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> about Whois Lookup</span><span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="wf-help-link">详细了解<span class="wf-hidden-xs">Whois 查询</span><span class="screen-reader-text">（在新标签页打开）</span></a>',' (host setting <a href="%s" class="wfhelp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>)'=>'（主机设置<a href="%s" class="wfhelp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><span class="screen-reader-text">（在新标签页打开）</span></a>）','<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="wf-help-link">Learn more<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> about Live Traffic</span><span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="wf-help-link">详细了解<span class="wf-hidden-xs">实时流量</span><span class="screen-reader-text">（在新标签页打开）</span></a>','<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="wf-help-link">Learn more<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> about importing and exporting options</span><span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="wf-help-link">详细了解<span class="wf-hidden-xs">导入和导出选项</span><span class="screen-reader-text">（在新标签页打开）</span></a>','<a href="%s" target="_blank">Click here<span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'<a href="%s" target="_blank">单击此处<span class="screen-reader-text"> (','opens in new tab'=>'在新标签页打开','Unknown (mixed plugin version)'=>'未知（混合插件版本）','Active WAF storage engine'=>'活动 WAF 存储引擎','Configured WAF storage engine (WFWAF_STORAGE_ENGINE)'=>'已配置的 WAF 存储引擎 (WFWAF_STORAGE_ENGINE)','The WAF storage engine is currently set to mysqli, but Wordfence is unable to use the database. The WAF will fall back to using local file system storage instead.'=>'WAF 存储引擎当前设置为 mysqli，但 Wordfence 无法使用该数据库。WAF 将退回到使用本地文件系统存储。','Tables missing (prefix %1$s, %2$s): %3$s'=>'表丢失（前缀 %1$s, %2$s）：%3$s','We could not write to %1$s. (%2$d bytes written) You may not have permission to modify files on your WordPress server.'=>'我们无法写入 %1$s。(已写入 %2$d 字节）您可能没有权限修改 WordPress 服务器上的文件。','Add Additional Signatures'=>'添加其他签名','Edit trusted proxies'=>'编辑受信任的代理','Your IP with this setting:'=>'使用此设置查看您的 IP：','Detected IP(s):'=>'检测到的 IP：','click here for help'=>'点击此处获取帮助','If you cannot complete the setup process, '=>'如果无法完成设置过程，','Error During Setup'=>'设置过程中出错','Enable country blocking by upgrading to Premium.'=>'通过升级到高级版启用国家 / 地区封锁。','You are running PHP version %1$s that is not supported by Wordfence %2$s. Wordfence features will not be available until PHP has been upgraded. We recommend using PHP version 8.1, but Wordfence will run on PHP version %3$s at a minimum.'=>'您运行的 PHP 版本 %1$s 不支持 Wordfence %2$s。在升级 PHP 之前，Wordfence 功能将不可用。我们建议使用 PHP 版本 8.1，但 Wordfence 至少可以在 PHP 版本 %3$s 上运行。','Go to'=>'转到','Go:'=>'转到','Scheduled time for day %s hour %s is: %s'=>'天 %s 小时 %s 的计划时间是：%s','Description: %s'=>'说明： %s','The issue type is: %s'=>'问题类型是：%s','No failed logins have been recorded.'=>'没有登录失败的记录。','No successful logins have been recorded.'=>'没有成功登录的记录。','Failed'=>'失败','Successful'=>'成功登录','We encountered an error trying load more data.'=>'加载更多数据时遇到错误。','Show more'=>'显示更多','7 Days'=>'7 天','Top IPs Blocked'=>'被阻止的顶级 IP','Total Attacks'=>'攻击总数','Connect This Site'=>'连接该网站','Reconnect This Site'=>'重新连接此站点','No notifications received'=>'未收到通知','Top Countries by Number of Attacks - Last 7 Days'=>'攻击次数最多的国家 - 最近 7 天','Date'=>'日期','License renews in 1 day'=>'许可证在 1 天内更新','License renews in %d days'=>'许可证在 %d 天后更新','License renews tomorrow'=>'许可证明天更新','License renews today'=>'许可证今天更新','Live Updates Paused &mdash; Click inside window to resume'=>'实时更新已暂停 - 点击窗口内侧恢复更新','Wordfence Live Activity:'=>'Wordfence 实时活动：','Wordfence activity for %1$s on %2$s'=>'%1$s 在 %2$s 上的 Wordfence 活动','Blocking IP %1$s. %2$s'=>'阻止 IP %1$s。%2$s','UA/Referrer/IP Range not allowed'=>'UA/Referrer/IP 范围不允许','getHits got invalid hitType: %s'=>'getHits got 无效 hitType：%s','Invalid log type to wfLog: %s'=>'发送到 wfLog 的无效日志类型：%s','Scan Engine Error: %s'=>'扫描引擎错误： %s','Scan terminated with error: %s'=>'扫描错误终止： %s','Initiating quick scan'=>'启动快速扫描','Deferring scheduled scan by %s'=>'推迟计划扫描 %s','Contacting Wordfence to initiate scan'=>'联系 Wordfence 以启动扫描','Previous scan terminated with an error. See below.'=>'上一次扫描因错误而终止。请参阅下文。','Scan can\'t continue - stored data not found after a fork. Got type: %s'=>'扫描无法继续 - 在分叉后未找到存储数据。得到类型：%s','Got a true deserialized value back from \'wfsd_engine\' with type: %s'=>'从类型为 %s 的「wfsd_engine」获取了一个真实的反序列化值','Setting up scanRunning and starting scan'=>'设置 scanRunning 并开始扫描','Setting up error handling environment'=>'设置错误处理环境','Requesting max memory'=>'请求最大内存','Using low resource scanning'=>'使用低资源扫描','There is already a scan running.'=>'已有扫描正在运行。','Checking if scan is already running'=>'检查扫描是否已在运行','Wordfence could not start a scan because the cron key does not match the saved key. Saved: %1$s Sent: %2$s Current unexploded: %3$s'=>'Wordfence 无法启动扫描，因为 cron 密钥与保存的密钥不匹配。已保存：%1$s 已发送：%2$s 当前未爆炸：%3$s','Checking saved cronkey against cronkey param'=>'根据 cronkey 参数检查已保存的 cronkey','Wordfence could not find a saved cron key to start the scan so assuming it started and exiting.'=>'Wordfence 无法找到用于启动扫描的已保存 cronkey，因此假定扫描已启动并退出。','The key used to start a scan expired. The value is: %1$s and split is: %2$s and time is: %3$d'=>'用于启动扫描的密钥已过期。值为：%1$s，分割为：%2$s，时间为：%3$d','Wordfence scan script accessed directly, or WF did not receive a cronkey.'=>'Wordfence 扫描脚本直接访问，或 WF 没有收到 cronkey。','Fetching stored cronkey for comparison.'=>'获取已存储的 cronkey 以进行比较。','Verifying start request signature.'=>'验证启动要求签名。','Scan engine received request.'=>'扫描引擎收到要求。','Cron test received and message printed'=>'收到 Cron 测试并打印信息','Looks like the Wordfence database tables have been deleted. You can fix this by de-activating and re-activating the Wordfence plugin from your Plugins menu.'=>'看起来 Wordfence 数据库表已被删除。您可以从插件菜单中停用并重新启用 Wordfence 插件来解决这个问题。','Could not connect to database to start scan: %s'=>'无法连接数据库以开始扫描：%s','File last modified:'=>'文件最后修改：','File Size:'=>'文件大小：','Wordfence: File Viewer'=>'Wordfence：文件查看器','Mode'=>'模式','The Wordfence server\'s response did not contain the expected elements.'=>'Wordfence 服务器的响应不包含预期的元素。','Unable to remove code execution protections applied to the .htaccess file in the uploads directory. Please check your permissions on that file.'=>'无法对上传目录中的 .htaccess 文件实施移除代码执行保护。请检查该文件的权限。','Unable to save the .htaccess file needed to disable script execution in the uploads directory. Please check your permissions on that directory.'=>'无法在 uploads 目录中保存禁用脚本执行所需的 .htaccess 文件。请检查该目录的权限。','Error finishing writing value for %1$s (MySQLi error: [%2$s] %3$s)'=>'为 %1$s 完成值时出错（MySQLi 错误：[%2$s] %3$s）','Error writing value for %1$s (MySQLi error: [%2$s] %3$s)'=>'为 %1$s 写入值时出错（MySQLi 错误：[%2$s] %3$s）','Error writing value header for %s'=>'为 %s 写入值头时出错','Error writing value chunk for %1$s (MySQLi error: [%2$s] %3$s)'=>'为 %1$s 写入值块时出错（MySQLi 错误：[%2$s] %3$s）','Error reassembling value for %s'=>'重新组装 %s 的值时出错','wfConfig::set() got an array as second param with key: %1$s and value: %2$s'=>'wfConfig::set() 的第二个参数是一个数组，键为 %1$s，值为 %2$s','The license you were using has been removed from your account. Please reach out to <a href="mailto:billing@wordfence.com">billing@wordfence.com</a> or create a Premium support case at <a href="https://support.wordfence.com/support/tickets" target="_blank">https://support.wordfence.com/support/tickets<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a> for more information. Our staff is happy to help.'=>'您使用的许可证已从您的账户中删除。请联系 <a href="mailto:billing@wordfence.com">billing@wordfence.com</a>，或在 <a href="https://support.wordfence.com/support/tickets" target="_blank">https://support.wordfence.com/support/tickets<span class="screen-reader-text">(在新标签页打开)</span></a>创建高级支持案例，了解更多信息。我们的员工很乐意提供帮助。','&copy;&nbsp;%1$d to %2$d Wordfence &mdash; Visit <a href="http://wordfence.com/">Wordfence.com</a> for help, security updates and more.'=>'© %1$d to %2$d Wordfence - 访问 <a href="http://wordfence.com/">Wordfence.com</a> 获取帮助、安全更新和更多信息。','There are no differences between the original file and the file in the repository.'=>'原始文件与存储库中的文件没有任何区别。','Unknown Type'=>'未知类型','Plugin Version:'=>'插件版本：','Plugin Name:'=>'插件名称：','Plugin File'=>'插件文件','Theme Version:'=>'主题版本','Theme Name:'=>'主题名称：','Theme File'=>'主题文件','WordPress Core File'=>'WordPress 核心文件','File type:'=>'文件类型：','Filename:'=>'文件名：','The two panels below show a before and after view of a file on your system that has been modified. The left panel shows the original file before modification. The right panel shows your version of the file that has been modified. Use this view to determine if a file has been modified by an attacker or if this is a change that you or another trusted person made. If you are happy with the modifications you see here, then you should choose to ignore this file the next time Wordfence scans your system.'=>'下面两个面板显示的是您系统上的文件修改前后的对比。左侧面板显示的是修改前的原始文件。右边的面板显示的是您的修改过的文件版本。使用该视图可确定文件是否被攻击者修改过，或者是否是你或其他可信人员所做的修改。如果您对这里的修改感到满意，那么下次 Wordfence 扫描您的系统时，您可以选择忽略此文件。','Wordfence: Viewing File Differences'=>'Wordfence：查看文件差异','Wordfence: All recent hits for IP address %s'=>'Wordfence：IP 地址 %s 的所有最近点击','We were unable to remove the <code>wordfence-waf.php</code> file in the root of the WordPress installation. It\'s possible WordPress cannot remove the <code>wordfence-waf.php</code> file because of file permissions. Please verify the permissions are correct and retry the removal.'=>'我们无法移除 WordPress 安装根目录中的 <code>wordfence-waf.php</code> 文件。可能是因为文件权限问题，WordPress 无法移除 <code>wordfence-waf.php</code> 文件。请确认权限无误后重试删除。','We were unable to make changes to the %1$s file. It\'s possible WordPress cannot write to the %1$s file because of file permissions. Please verify the permissions are correct and retry the installation.'=>'我们无法更改 %1$s 文件。由于文件权限问题，WordPress 可能无法写入 %1$s 文件。请检查权限是否正确，然后重试安装。','We were unable to make changes to the .htaccess file. It\'s possible WordPress cannot write to the .htaccess file because of file permissions, which may have been set by another security plugin, or you may have set them manually. Please verify the permissions allow the web server to write to the file, and retry the installation.'=>'我们无法更改 .htaccess 文件。WordPress 无法写入 .htaccess 文件可能是因为文件权限的问题，这可能是由其他安全插件设置的，也可能是您手动设置的。请确认权限允许网络服务器写入文件，然后重试安装。','We were unable to create the <code>wordfence-waf.php</code> file in the root of the WordPress installation. It\'s possible WordPress cannot write to the <code>wordfence-waf.php</code> file because of file permissions. Please verify the permissions are correct and retry the installation.'=>'我们无法在 WordPress 安装根目录下创建 <code>wordfence-waf.php</code> 文件。由于文件权限问题，WordPress 可能无法写入 <code>wordfence-waf.php</code> 文件。请确认权限无误后重试安装。','The update was successful!'=>'更新成功！','Blocked for %1$s in file: %2$s = %3$s'=>'在文件中 %1$s 被阻止： %2$s = %3$s','Blocked for %1$s in cookie: %2$s = %3$s'=>'cookie 中的 %1$s 被阻止： %2$s = %3$s','Blocked for %1$s in POST body: %2$s = %3$s'=>'在 POST 主体中阻止 %1$s: %2$s = %3$s','Blocked for %1$s in query string: %2$s = %3$s'=>'查询字符串中的 %1$s 被阻止： %2$s = %3$s','Blocked for %s'=>'因 %s 而被阻止','Blocked because the IP is blocklisted'=>'因 IP 已被列入封堵名单而被封堵','Allowlisted via Live Traffic'=>'通过实时流量列入允许列表','The WAF is currently in read-only mode and will not save any configuration changes.'=>'WAF 当前处于只读模式，不会保存任何配置更改。','Required parameters not sent.'=>'未发送所需的参数。','There was an error writing to your .htaccess file.'=>'写入 .htaccess 文件时出错。','Updating the .htaccess did not fix the issue. You may need to add <code>Options -Indexes</code> to your httpd.conf if using Apache, or find documentation on how to disable directory listing for your web server.'=>'更新 .htaccess 无法解决问题。如果使用 Apache，您可能需要在 httpd.conf 中添加<code>选项 -Indexes</code>，或者查找有关如何禁用网络服务器目录列表的文档。','Wordfence could not find your .htaccess file.'=>'Wordfence 无法找到您的 .htaccess 文件。','This user\'s email is the network admin email. It will need to be changed before deleting this user.'=>'该用户的邮箱是网络管理邮箱。在删除该用户之前，需要对其进行更改。','We could not find that user in the database.'=>'我们无法在数据库中找到该用户。','Wordfence activity in the past %s'=>'过去 %s 的 Wordfence 活动','Test email failed to send'=>'测试邮箱发送失败','Test email sent successfully'=>'测试邮箱发送成功','The IP you provided must be in dotted quad notation or use ranges with square brackets. e.g. 10.11.12.13 or 10.11.12.[1-50]'=>'您提供的 IP 必须使用点四符号或使用带方括号的范围，例如 [1-50] 0.[1-50][1-50].[1-50] 2.[1-50] 3 或 [1-50] 0.[1-50][1-50].[1-50] 2.#[1-50]','There was an error deleting the file.'=>'删除文件时出现错误。','The file <code>%s</code> was deleted successfully.'=>'文件<code>%s</code> 已成功删除。','Return to scan results'=>'返回扫描结果','There was an error restoring the file.'=>'恢复文件时出现错误。','The file <code>%s</code> was restored successfully.'=>'文件<code>%s</code> 已成功恢复。','If you want to reenable Wordfence Live Traffic, you need to deactivate %1$s and then go to the Wordfence options page and reenable Live Traffic there. Wordfence does work with %1$s, however Live Traffic will be disabled and the Wordfence firewall will also count less hits per visitor because of the %1$s caching function. All other functions should work correctly.'=>'如果您想重新启用 Wordfence 实时流量，您需要停用 %1$s，然后进入 Wordfence 选项页面，在那里重新启用实时流量。Wordfence 确实可以使用 %1$s，但是实时流量将被禁用，而且由于 %1$s 的缓存功能，Wordfence 防火墙对每个访客的点击次数也会减少。所有其他功能都应正常工作。','The Wordfence Live Traffic feature has been disabled because you have %s active which is not compatible with Wordfence Live Traffic.'=>'Wordfence 实时流量功能已被禁用，因为您已启用 %s，与 Wordfence 实时流量不兼容。','An error occured when fetching the WAF configuration from the database.'=>'从数据库获取 WAF 配置时发生错误。','We were unable to write to %s which the WAF uses for storage. Please update permissions on the parent directory so the web server can write to it.'=>'我们无法写入 WAF 用于存储的 %s。请更新父目录的权限，以便 web 服务器可以写入。','<a href="%s">Click here</a> to rebuild the configuration file.'=>'<a href="%s">单击此处</a>重建配置文件。','Malware URLs'=>'恶意软件 URL','JavaScript Errors'=>'JavaScript 错误','Notifications'=>'通知','You have %d new Wordfence notification.'=>'您有 %d 新 Wordfence 通知。','No thanks.'=>'不，谢谢。','Yes, enable auto-update.'=>'是的，启用自动更新。','Do you want Wordfence to stay up-to-date automatically?'=>'您希望 Wordfence 自动更新吗？','to manually update it.'=>'要手动更新。','visit the options page'=>'访问选项页面','or'=>'或','Click here to use the recommended setting'=>'点击此处使用推荐设置','Your \'How does Wordfence get IPs\' setting is misconfigured.'=>'您的「Wordfence 如何获取 IP」设置有误。','This site is currently using the Cloudflare "CF-Connecting-IP" HTTP header, which should only be used when the site is behind Cloudflare.'=>'该网站目前正在使用 Cloudflare 的「CF-Connecting-IP」HTTP 头信息，只有当网站位于 Cloudflare 后方时才可使用。','This site is currently using the X-Real-IP HTTP header, which should only be used when the site is behind a front-end proxy that outputs this header.'=>'本网站目前使用 X-Real-IP HTTP 标头，只有当本网站位于输出该标头的前端代理之后时，才可使用该标头。','This site is currently using the X-Forwarded-For HTTP header, which should only be used when the site is behind a front-end proxy that outputs this header.'=>'本网站目前正在使用 X-Forwarded-For HTTP 头信息，只有当本网站位于输出该头信息的前端代理之后时，才可使用该头信息。','This site is currently using PHP\'s built in REMOTE_ADDR.'=>'本网站目前使用 PHP 内置的 REMOTE_ADDR。','It is not currently in extended protection mode but was configured to use an older version of PHP and may have become deactivated when PHP was updated. You may perform the configuration update automatically by <a href="%1$s">clicking here</a> or use the "Optimize the Wordfence Firewall" button on the Firewall Options page. <a class="wfhelp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%2$s"><span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'它目前不在扩展保护模式中，但被配置为使用旧版本的 PHP，可能在 PHP 更新时被停用。您可以通过<a href="%1$s">单击此处</a>或使用防火墙选项页面上的 "优化 Wordfence 防火墙 "按钮自动执行配置更新。<a class="wfhelp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%2$s"><span class="screen-reader-text">(','It is currently configured to use an older version of PHP and may become deactivated if PHP is updated. You may perform the configuration update automatically by <a href="%1$s">clicking here</a>. <a class="wfhelp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%2$s"><span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'当前配置使用的是旧版本的 PHP，如果 PHP 更新，可能会停用。您可以通过<a href="%1$s">单击此处</a>自动执行配置更新。<a class="wfhelp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%2$s"><span class="screen-reader-text">(','The configuration files are corrupt or inaccessible by the web server, which is preventing the WAF from functioning. Please verify the web server has permission to access the configuration files. You may also try to rebuild the configuration file by <a href="%1$s">clicking here</a>. It will automatically resume normal operation when it is fixed. <a class="wfhelp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%2$s"><span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'配置文件已损坏或网络服务器无法访问，导致 WAF 无法运行。请确认网络服务器是否有权限访问配置文件。您也可以<a href="%1$s">点击这里</a>尝试重建配置文件。修复后，它将自动恢复正常运行。<a class="wfhelp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="%2$s"><span class="screen-reader-text">(','Wordfence generated an error on activation. The output we received during activation was:'=>'Wordfence 在激活时产生错误。我们在激活时收到的输出是','locked out from logging in'=>'已锁定无法登录','blocked for %s'=>'因 %s 而被阻止','blocked by the Wordfence Security Network'=>'被 Wordfence 安全网络阻止','blocked by real-time IP blocklist'=>'被实时 IP 阻止列表阻止','blocked by firewall for %s'=>'因 %s 被防火墙阻止','blocked by firewall'=>'被防火墙阻止','Your test email was sent to the requested email address. The result we received from the WordPress wp_mail() function was: %s<br /><br />A \'True\' result means WordPress thinks the mail was sent without errors. A \'False\' result means that WordPress encountered an error sending your mail. Note that it\'s possible to get a \'True\' response with an error elsewhere in your mail system that may cause emails to not be delivered.'=>'您的测试邮件已发送至请求的邮箱地址。我们从 WordPress wp_mail() 函数收到的结果是：%s<br /><br />\'真\'表示 WordPress 认为邮件已无错误发送。假 "结果表示 WordPress 在发送邮件时遇到了错误。请注意，如果您的邮件系统中其他地方出错，也有可能得到 "True "的响应，从而导致邮件无法送达。','Your rules have been updated successfully. You are currently using the free version of Wordfence. Upgrade to Wordfence premium to have your rules updated automatically as new threats emerge. <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/wafUpdateRules1/wordfence-signup/">Click here to purchase a premium license</a>. <em>Note: Your rules will still update every 30 days as a free user.</em>'=>'您的规则已成功更新。您目前使用的是 Wordfence 免费版。升级到 Wordfence 高级版，您的规则将在新威胁出现时自动更新。<a href="https://www.wordfence.com/wafUpdateRules1/wordfence-signup/">点击此处购买高级许可证</a>。<em>注意：作为免费用户，您的规则仍将每 30 天更新一次。</em>','Your rules have been updated successfully.'=>'您的规则已成功更新。','Your Wordfence activity log was sent to %s'=>'您的 Wordfence 活动日志已发送至 %s','Your .htaccess has been updated successfully. Please verify your site is functioning normally.'=>'您的 .htaccess 已更新成功。请确认您的网站运行正常。','You have unsaved changes to your options. If you leave this page, those changes will be lost.'=>'您的选项有未保存的更改。如果您离开此页面，这些更改将丢失。','You forgot to include a reason you\'re blocking this IP range. We ask you to include this for your own record keeping.'=>'您忘记说明封禁此 IP 范围的原因。我们要求您写明原因，以便保存记录。','You are using an Nginx web server and using a FastCGI processor like PHP5-FPM. You will need to manually modify your php.ini to disable <em>display_error</em>'=>'您使用的是 Nginx 网络服务器，并使用了类似 PHP5-FPM 的 FastCGI 处理器。您需要手动修改 php.ini，禁用 <em>display_error</em> 。','You are using an Nginx web server and using a FastCGI processor like PHP5-FPM. You will need to manually delete or hide those files.'=>'您使用的是 Nginx 网络服务器，并使用了类似 PHP5-FPM 的 FastCGI 处理器。您需要手动删除或隐藏这些文件。','You are using Nginx as your web server. You\'ll need to disable autoindexing in your nginx.conf. See the <a target=\'_blank\'  rel=\'noopener noreferrer\' href=\'http