n posts we scanned for dangerous websites'=>'检查在文章中发现的 URL，我们扫描了危险的网站','This post contains code that is suspicious. Please check the title of the post and confirm that the code in the title is not malicious.'=>'该文章包含可疑代码。请检查该文章的标题，并确认标题中的代码并非恶意代码。','Post title contains suspicious code'=>'文章标题包含可疑代码','Scanning posts with %d left to scan.'=>'扫描文章，还剩 %d。','Scanning posts for URLs on a domain blocklist'=>'扫描文章域名拦截列表中的 URL','Publicly accessible quarantined file found: %s'=>'发现可公开访问的隔离文件： %s','Testing accessibility of: %s'=>'Testing 无障碍 of：%s','Scanning for publicly accessible quarantined files'=>'扫描可公开访问的被隔离文件','Adding issue: %s'=>'添加问题： %s','Done file contents scan'=>'完成文件内容扫描','Starting scan of file contents'=>'开始扫描文件内容','Skipping scan of file contents for URLs on a domain blocklist'=>'跳过扫描文件内容中的域名拦截列表上的 URL','Scanning file contents for URLs on a domain blocklist'=>'扫描文件内容，查找域名拦截列表上的 URL','Skipping scan of file contents for infections and vulnerabilities'=>'跳过对文件内容的感染和漏洞扫描','Scanning file contents for infections and vulnerabilities'=>'扫描文件内容以查找感染和漏洞','Found %d theme'=>'发现 %d 主题','Getting theme list from WordPress'=>'从 WordPress 获取主题列表','Found %d plugin'=>'发现 %d 插件','Getting plugin list from WordPress'=>'从 WordPress 获取插件列表','Including files that are outside the WordPress installation in the scan.'=>'在扫描中包括 WordPress 安装之外的文件。','Checking for paths skipped due to scan settings'=>'由于扫描设置而跳过的路径检查','Wordfence could not read the content of your WordPress directory. This usually indicates your permissions are so strict that your web server can\'t read your WordPress directory.'=>'Wordfence 无法读取 WordPress 目录的内容。这通常表明您的权限过于严格，以至于网络服务器无法读取 WordPress 目录。','Check if your site is being Spamvertized is for paid members only'=>'检查您的网站是否被垃圾邮件 vertized 仅限付费会员使用','Checking if your site is being Spamvertised'=>'检查您的网站是否被垃圾邮件宣传','Directory listing provides an attacker with the complete index of all the resources located inside of the directory. The specific risks and consequences vary depending on which files are listed and accessible, but it is recommended that you disable it unless it is needed.'=>'目录列表为攻击者提供了目录内所有资源的完整索引。具体风险和后果因所列出和可访问的文件而异，但建议除非有必要，否则禁用它。','Directory listing is enabled'=>'目录列表已启用','Full Path Disclosure (FPD) vulnerabilities enable the attacker to see the path to the webroot/file. e.g.: /home/user/htdocs/file/. Certain vulnerabilities, such as using the load_file() (within a SQL Injection) query to view the page source, require the attacker to have the full path to the file they wish to view.'=>'全路径披露 (FPD) 漏洞启用后，攻击者可以看到 webroot/ 文件的路径：/home/user/htdocs/ 文件 /。某些漏洞，如使用 load_文件 ()（在 SQL 注入中）查询来查看页面源代码，需要攻击者拥有他们想要查看的完整路径文件。','Web server exposes the document root'=>'网络服务器公开文件根目录','Checking if your server discloses the path to the document root'=>'检查您的服务器是否向文档根公开了路径','<a href="%1$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">%1$s</a> is publicly accessible and may expose source code or sensitive information about your site. Files such as this one are commonly checked for by scanners and should be made inaccessible. Alternately, some can be removed if you are certain your site does not need them. Sites using the nginx web server may need manual configuration changes to protect such files. <a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Learn more<span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'<a href="%1$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">%1$s</a> 是可公开访问的，可能会暴露源代码或有关您网站的敏感性信息。像这样的文件通常会被扫描程序检查到，因此应使其无法访问。另外，如果确定网站不需要某些文件，也可以将其删除。使用 nginx 网络服务器的网站可能需要手动更改配置以保护此类文件。<a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">了解更多 <span class="screen-reader-text">(','Publicly accessible config, backup, or log file found: %s'=>'发现可公开访问的配置、备份或日志文件: %s','Check for publicly accessible configuration files, backup files and logs'=>'检查是否有可公开访问的配置文件、备份文件和日志','A test request to this website was detected on a different value for this setting. IP blocking and live traffic information may not be accurate. <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Get More Information<span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'在此设置的不同值上检测到了对该网站的测试要求。IP 拦截和实时流量信息可能不准确。<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">获取更多信息 <span class="screen-reader-text">(','\'How does Wordfence get IPs\' is misconfigured'=>'「Wordfence 如何获取 IP」配置错误','This site appears to be behind Cloudflare, so using the Cloudflare "CF-Connecting-IP" HTTP header will resolve to the correct IPs.'=>'本网站似乎位于 Cloudflare 后台，因此使用 Cloudflare「CF-Connecting-IP」 HTTP 标头可以解析到正确的 IP。','This site appears to be behind a front-end proxy, so using the X-Real-IP HTTP header will resolve to the correct IPs.'=>'该网站似乎位于前端代理之后，因此使用 X-Real-IP HTTP 标头可以解析到正确的 IP。','This site appears to be behind a front-end proxy, so using the X-Forwarded-For HTTP header will resolve to the correct IPs.'=>'本网站似乎位于前端代理之后，因此使用 X-Forwarded-For HTTP 标头可以解析到正确的 IP。','For maximum security use PHP\'s built in REMOTE_ADDR.'=>'要获得最大的安全性，请使用 PHP 内置的 REMOTE_ADDR。','Wordfence was unable to validate a test request to your website. This can happen if your website is behind a proxy that does not use one of the standard ways to convey the IP of the request or it is unreachable publicly. IP blocking and live traffic information may not be accurate. <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Get More Information<span class="screen-reader-text"> ('=>'Wordfence 无法验证您网站的测试要求。如果您的网站在代理服务器后面，而代理服务器没有使用标准方式之一来传送要求的 IP，或者无法公开访问，就会出现这种情况。IP 拦截和实时流量信息可能不准确。<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">获取更多信息 <span class="screen-reader-text">(','Unable to accurately detect IPs'=>'无法准确检测 IP','Checking for the most secure way to get IPs'=>'检查获取 IP 的最安全方法','The URL is: %s'=>'URL 是 %s','Your site is listed on a domain blocklist.'=>'您的网站已被列入域名封锁名单。','The multisite blog with ID %d is listed on a domain blocklist.'=>'ID 为 %d 的多站点博客已被列入域名拦截列表。','The URL %s is on the blocklist.'=>'URL %s 在拦截列表中。','Your site is listed on the Wordfence domain blocklist.'=>'您的网站被列入 Wordfence 域名拦截列表。','The multisite blo