ashboard'=>'前往仪表盘','If you don\'t have one, you can purchase one now.'=>'如果您没有，可以立即购买。','Install'=>'安装','Enter Premium Key'=>'输入高级密钥','Enter your premium license key to enable real-time protection for your website.'=>'输入您的高级许可证密钥，以便为您的网站启用实时保护。','Activate Premium'=>'激活高级版','Please Complete Wordfence Installation'=>'请完成 Wordfence 安装','Uninstallation from this site was successful! The Wordfence Firewall is still active because it is installed in another WordPress installation.'=>'从这个网站卸载成功！ Wordfence 防火墙仍处于活动状态，因为它安装在另一个 WordPress 安装中。','Uninstallation was successful!'=>'卸载成功！','HTML tags will be stripped prior to output and line breaks will be converted into the appropriate tags.'=>'HTML 元素标签将在输出之前被剥离，换行符将被转换为适当的标记。','Prevent discovery of usernames through \'/?author=N\' scans, the oEmbed API, the WordPress REST API, and WordPress XML Sitemaps'=>'防止通过「/?author=N」扫描、oEmbed API、WordPress REST API 和 WordPress XML 站点地图发现用户名','Prevent users registering \'admin\' username if it doesn\'t exist'=>'屏蔽用户注册「admin」用户名 (如果不存在)','Force all members to use strong passwords'=>'强制所有成员使用强密码','Force admins and publishers to use strong passwords (recommended)'=>'强制管理员和发布者使用强密码（推荐）','Additional Options'=>'其他选项','For all users with "publish posts" capability'=>'适用于具有「发布文章」功能的所有用户','For admins only'=>'仅限超级管理员','Hit enter to add a username'=>'按 Enter 键添加用户名','This option enables all "Brute Force Protection" options, including strong password enforcement and invalid login throttling. You can modify individual options below.'=>'此选项支持所有「暴力破解保护」选项，包括强密码强制和无效登录限制。您可以修改下面的单个选项。','Once you have downloaded the files, click Continue to complete uninstallation.'=>'下载文件后，单击「继续」以完成卸载。','We\'ve preselected your server configuration based on our tests, but if you know your web server\'s configuration, please select it now.'=>'我们已根据测试预先选择了您的服务器配置，但如果您知道自己的 Web 服务器配置，请立即选择。','Before this file can be deleted, the configuration for the <code>auto_prepend_file</code> setting needs to be removed.'=>'在此文件可以删除之前，配置为 <code>auto_prepend_file</code> 设置需要删除。','Extended Protection Mode of the Wordfence Web Application Firewall uses the PHP ini setting called <code>auto_prepend_file</code> in order to ensure it runs before any potentially vulnerable code runs. This PHP setting currently refers to the Wordfence file at:'=>'Wordfence 的扩展保护模式 Web 应用进程防火墙使用名为的 PHP INI 设置 <code>auto_prepend_file</code> 以确保它在任何可能存在漏洞的代码运行之前运行。 此 PHP 设置当前引用 Wordfence 文件：','Uninstall Wordfence Firewall'=>'卸载 Wordfence 防火墙','Once you have downloaded the files, click Continue to complete the setup.'=>'下载文件后，单击「继续」以完成设置。','Download %s'=>'下载 %s','Please download a backup of the following files before we make the necessary changes:'=>'在进行必要的更改之前，请下载以下文件的备份：','If you are using a web server not listed in the dropdown or if file permissions prevent the installer from completing successfully, you will need to perform the change manually. Click Continue below to create the required file and view manual installation instructions.'=>'如果您使用的是下拉列表中未列出的 Web 服务器，或者文件权限阻止安装进程成功完成，则需要手动执行更改。 单击下面的继续以创建所需文件并查看手动安装说明。','Part of the Firewall configuration procedure for NGINX depends on creating a <code>%1$s</code> file in the root of your WordPress installation. This file can contain sensitive information and public access to it should be restricted. We have <a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">instructions on our documentation site<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a> on what directives to put in your nginx.conf to fix this.'=>'NGINX 防火墙配置过程的一部分取决于在 WordPress 安装的根目录中创建 <code>%1$s</code> 文件。此文件可能包含敏感信息，应限制对它的公共访问。我们的<a href="%2$s" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">文档站点<span class="screen-reader-text">（在新标签页打开）</span></a>上提供了有关在 nginx.conf 中放入哪些指令以解决此问题的说明。','We\'ve preselected your server configuration based on our tests, but if you know your web server\'s configuration, please select it now. You can also choose "Manual Configuration" for alternate installation details.'=>'我们已根据测试预先选择了您的服务器配置，但如果您知道自己的 Web 服务器配置，请立即选择。 您也可以选择「手动配置」以获取备用安装详细信息。','If you know your web server\'s configuration, please select it from the list below.'=>'如果您知道 Web 服务器的配置，请从下面的列表中选择它。','Manual Configuration'=>'手工配置','Windows (IIS)'=>'Windows (IIS)','NGINX'=>'NGINX','LiteSpeed/lsapi'=>'LiteSpeed/lsapi','Apache + CGI/FastCGI'=>'Apache + CGI/FastCGI','Apache + suPHP'=>'Apache + suPHP','Apache + mod_php'=>'Apache + mod_php','If you have separate WordPress installations with Wordfence installed within a subdirectory of this site, it is recommended that you perform the Firewall installation procedure on those sites before this one.'=>'如果您在此站点的子目录中安装了单独的 Wordfress 安装 Wordfence，则建议您在此站点之前对这些站点执行防火墙安装过程。','NOTE:'=>'注意:','Override'=>'覆盖','Include'=>'包括','You can proceed with the installation and we will include this from within our <code>wordfence-waf.php</code> file which should maintain compatibility with your site, or you can opt to override the existing PHP setting.'=>'您可以继续安装，我们将在<code> wordfence-waf.php </code>文件中包含此文件，该文件应与您的站点保持兼容，或者您可以选择覆盖现有的 PHP 设置。','To make your site as secure as possible, the Wordfence Web Application Firewall is designed to run via a PHP setting called <code>auto_prepend_file</code>, which ensures it runs before any potentially vulnerable code runs. This PHP setting is currently in use, and is including this file:'=>'为了使您的站点尽可能安全，Wordfence Web 应用进程防火墙旨在通过名为的 PHP 设置运行 <code>auto_prepend_file</code>，确保它在任何可能存在漏洞的代码运行之前运行。 此 PHP 设置当前正在使用，并包含此文件：','To make your site as secure as possible, the Wordfence Web Application Firewall is designed to run via a PHP setting called <code>auto_prepend_file</code>, which ensures it runs before any potentially vulnerable code runs.'=>'为了使您的站点尽可能安全，Wordfence Web 应用进程防火墙旨在通过名为的 PHP 设置运行 <code>auto_prepend_file</code>，确保它在任何可能存在漏洞的代码运行之前运行。','Optimize Wordfence Firewall'=>'优化 Wordfence 防火墙','then'=>'然后','This feature blocks all traffic from IPs with a high volume of recent malicious activity using Wordfence\'s real-time blocklist.'=>'此功能使用 Wordfence 的实时黑名单阻止来自具有大量近期恶意活动的 IP 的所有流量。','Premium Feature:'=>'高级功能：','The plugin will load as a regular plugin after WordPress has been loaded, and while it can block many malicious requests, some vulnerable plugins or WordPress itself may run vulnerable code before all plugins are loaded.'=>'该插件将在加载 WordPress 后作为常规插件加载，虽然它可以阻止许多恶意请求，但是一些易受攻击的插件或 WordPress 本身可能会在加载所有插件之前运行易受攻击的代码。','Basic WordPress Protection:'=>'基本的 WordPress 保护：','Optimize the Wordfence Firewall'=>'优化 Wordfence 防火墙','You are currently running the Wordfence Web Application Firewall from another WordPress installation. Please configure the firewall to run correctly on this site.'=>'您当前正在从另一个 WordPress 安装运行 Wordfence Web 应用进程防火墙。 请将防火墙配置为在此站点上正确运行。','Existing WAF Installation Detected:'=>'检测到现有 WAF 安装：','Remove Extended Protection'=>'删除扩展保护','If you\'re moving to a new host or a new installation location, you may need to temporarily disable extended protection to avoid any file not found errors. Use this action to remove the configuration changes that enable extended protection mode or you can <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">remove them manually<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>.'=>'如果您要移至新主机或新安装位置，则可能需要暂时禁用扩展保护以避免出现任何文件未找到错误。使用此操作可移除启用扩展保护模式的配置更改，或者您可以<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">手动移除它们<span class="screen-reader-text">（在新标签页打开）</span></a>。','All PHP requests will be processed by the firewall prior to running.'=>'所有 PHP 请求都将在运行之前由防火墙处理。','Extended Protection:'=>'扩展保护：','Protection Level'=>'保护等级','Automatically enable on'=>'自动启用','Enabled and Protecting'=>'启用和保护','In this mode, the Wordfence Web Application Firewall is functionally turned off and does not run any of its rules or analyze the request in any way.'=>'在此模式下，Wordfence Web 应用进程防火墙在功能上处于关闭状态，不会运行任何规则或以任何方式分析请求。','Disabled:'=>'禁用：','When you first install the Wordfence Web Application Firewall, it will be in learning mode. This allows Wordfence to learn about your site so that we can understand how to protect it and how to allow normal visitors through the firewall. We recommend you let Wordfence learn for a week before you enable the firewall. <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Learn More<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'首次安装 Wordfence Web 应用程序防火墙时，它将处于学习模式。这允许 Wordfence 了解您的网站，以便我们了解如何保护它以及如何允许普通访问者通过防火墙。我们建议您在启用防火墙之前让 Wordfence 学习一周。<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">了解更多<span class="screen-reader-text">（在新标签页打开）</span></a>','Learning Mode:'=>'学习模式：','In this mode, the Wordfence Web Application Firewall is actively blocking requests matching known attack patterns and is actively protecting your site from attackers.'=>'在此模式下，Wordfence Web 应用进程防火墙主动阻止与已知攻击模式匹配的请求，并主动保护您的站点免受攻击者攻击。','Enabled and Protecting:'=>'启用和保护：','Basic Firewall Options'=>'基本防火墙选项','SHOW ALL RULES'=>'显示所有规则','<a href="#" onclick="WFAD.wafUpdateRules();return false;" role="button">Click here</a> to pull down the latest from the Wordfence servers.'=>'<a href="#" onclick="WFAD.wafUpdateRules();return false;">单击此处</a>以从 Wordfence 服务器下载最新版本。','No rules currently set.'=>'暂未设置规则。','Description'=>'描述','Category'=>'分类','Ignored IPs must be separated by commas or placed on separate lines. These addresses will be ignored from any alerts about increased attacks and can be used to ignore things like standalone website security scanners.'=>'被忽略的 IP 地址必须使用英文逗号分隔或放在单独的行上。 这些地址将在任何有关攻击增加的警报中被忽略，并可用于忽略独立网站安全扫描进程等内容。','Separate multiple URLs with commas or place them on separate lines. Asterisks are wildcards, but use with care. If you see an attacker repeatedly probing your site for a known vulnerability you can use this to immediately block them. All URLs must start with a "/" without quotes and must be relative. e.g. /badURLone/, /bannedPage.html, /dont-access/this/URL/, /starts/with-*'=>'用英文逗号分隔多个 URL 或将它们放在不同的行上。 星号*是通配符，但要小心使用。 如果您发现攻击者反复探测您的网站是否存在已知漏洞，则可以使用此漏洞立即阻止它们。 所有网址必须以「/」开头，不带引号，且必须是相对地址的。 例如 /badURLone/,/bannedPage.html,/dont-access/this/URL/,/starts/with-*','Allowlisted IPs must be separated by commas or placed on separate lines. You can specify ranges using the following formats: 127.0.0.1/24, 127.0.0.[1-100], or 127.0.0.1-127.0.1.100<br/>Wordfence automatically allowlists <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Private_network" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">private networks<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a> because these are not routable on the public Internet.'=>'列入白名单的 IP 必须用逗号分隔或放在单独的行上。您可以使用以下格式指定范围：127.0.0.1/24、127.0.0.[1-100] 或 127.0.0.1-127.0.1.100<br/>Wordfence 会自动将<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Private_network" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">私有网络<span class="screen-reader-text">（在新标签页打开）</span></a>列入白名单，因为这些网络在公共互联网上无法路由。','You are currently running the WAF from another WordPress installation. This option can be changed once you configure the firewall to run correctly on this site.'=>'您当前正在从另一个 WordPress 安装中运行 WAF。 将防火墙配置为在此站点上正确运行后，可以更改此选项。','Advanced Firewall Options'=>'高级防火墙选项','No allowlisted URLs currently set.'=>'当前未设置列入白名单的网址。','Toggle row ${idx}'=>'切换行 ${idx}','Select row ${idx}'=>'选择行 ${idx}','Created'=>'创建','Select/deselect all'=>'选择 / 取消全选','Monitor background requests from an administrator\'s web browser for false positives'=>'监视来自管理员 Web 浏览器的后台请求以获取误报','Admin Panel'=>'管理面板','Front-end Website'=>'前端网站','You are currently running the Wordfence Web Application Firewall from another WordPress installation. Please <a href="%s">click here</a> to configure the Firewall to run correctly on this site.'=>'您当前正在从另一个 WordPress 安装运行 Wordfence Web 应用进程防火墙。 请<a href="%s">单击此处</a>以将防火墙配置为在此站点上正确运行。','The required file has been created. You\'ll need to insert the following code into your <code>php.ini</code> to finish installation:'=>'已创建所需的文件。 您需要将以下代码插入<code> php.ini </code>以完成安装：','The changes have not yet taken effect. If you are using LiteSpeed or IIS as your web server or CGI/FastCGI interface, you may need to wait a few minutes for the changes to take effect since the configuration files are sometimes cached. You also may need to select a different server configuration in order to complete this step, but wait for a few minutes before trying. You can try refreshing this page.'=>'这些变化尚未生效。 如果您使用 LiteSpeed 或 IIS 作为 Web 服务器或 CGI / FastCGI 接口，则可能需要等待几分钟才能使更改生效，因为配置文件有时会被缓存。 您还可能需要选择其他服务器配置才能完成此步骤，但在尝试之前请等待几分钟。 您可以尝试刷新此页面。','Nice work! The firewall is now optimized.'=>'干得好！ 防火墙现在已经过优化。','Premium Protection Enabled'=>'高级安全防护已启用','<i class="wf-fa wf-fa-lightbulb-o wf-tip" aria-hidden="true"></i> When you first install the Wordfence Web Application Firewall, it will be in learning mode. This allows Wordfence to learn about your site so that we can understand how to protect it and how to allow normal visitors through the firewall. We recommend you let Wordfence learn for a week before you enable the firewall.'=>'<i class="wf-fa wf-fa-lightbulb-o wf-tip" aria-hidden="true"></i>首次安装 Wordfence Web 应用进程防火墙时，它将处于学习模式。 这允许 Wordfence 了解您的网站，以便我们了解如何保护它以及如何允许普通访问者通过防火墙。 我们建议您在启用防火墙之前让 Wordfence 学习一周。','Learning Mode Until %s'=>'学习模式直到 %s','Learning Mode Enabled'=>'学习模式已启用','Wordfence Firewall Activated'=>'Wordfence 防火墙已启用','Enable Firewall'=>'启用防火墙','The Wordfence Web Application Firewall is a PHP-based, application-level firewall that filters out malicious requests to your site. It is designed to run at the beginning of WordPress\' initialization to filter any attacks before plugins or themes can run any potentially vulnerable code.'=>'Wordfence Web 应用进程防火墙是一个基于 PHP 的应用进程级防火墙，可以过滤掉对您站点的恶意请求。 它被设计为在 WordPress 初始化时运行，以在插件或主题可以运行任何可能易受攻击的代码之前过滤任何攻击。','Wordfence Firewall Deactivated'=>'Wordfence 防火墙已停用','Wordfence Firewall &amp; Premium Enabled'=>'Wordfence 防火墙&amp;高级版已启用','These URL patterns will be excluded from the throttling rules used to limit crawlers.'=>'这些 URL 模式将从用于限制爬网进程的限制规则中排除。','block it'=>'屏蔽它','throttle it'=>'节流它','%d per minute'=>'%d/ 每分钟','Treat Google like any other Crawler'=>'像任何其他 Crawler 一样对待 Google','Anyone claiming to be Google will not be rate-limited'=>'任何自称是 Google 的人不会受到比率限制','Verified Google crawlers will not be rate-limited'=>'已验证的 Google 爬虫程序不会受比率限制','NOTE: This checkbox enables ALL blocking/throttling functions including IP, country and advanced blocking, and the "Rate Limiting Rules" below.'=>'注意：此复选框启用所有阻止 / 限制功能，包括 IP，国家和高级阻止，以及下面的「速率限制规则」。','Manually Refresh Rules'=>'手动刷新规则','You are currently running the WAF from another WordPress installation. These rules can be disabled or enabled once you configure the firewall to run correctly on this site.'=>'您当前正在从另一个 WordPress 安装中运行 WAF。 将防火墙配置为在此站点上正确运行后，可以禁用或启用这些规则。','Rules'=>'规则','Filter Value'=>'筛选值','IP'=>'IP','User'=>'用户','Source'=>'来源','Param'=>'参数','Disable'=>'禁用','Delete'=>'删除','Allowlisted via Firewall Options page'=>'通过防火墙选项页面列入白名单','An allowlist entry for this URL and parameter already exists.'=>'此网址和参数的白名单条目已存在。','Add'=>'添加','Param Name'=>'参数名称','Query String'=>'查询字符串','Header'=>'页眉','File Name'=>'文件名称','Cookie'=>'Cookie','POST Body'=>'POST Body','URL'=>'网址','The URL/parameters in this table will not be tested by the firewall. They are typically added while the firewall is in Learning Mode or by an admin who identifies a particular action/request is a false positive.'=>'防火墙不会测试此表中的 URL / 参数。 它们通常在防火墙处于学习模式时添加，或者由识别特定操作 / 请求的管理员添加为误报。','Add Allowlisted URL/Param'=>'添加白名单 URL / 参数','<br><strong>This setting will be ignored because the PHP configuration option <code>output_buffering</code> is off.</strong>'=>'<br><strong>由于 PHP 配置选项，此设置将被忽略 <code>output_buffering</code> 已关闭。</strong>','<strong>Enable Separate Prompt for Two-Factor Code<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="wfhelp wf-inline-help"><span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a></strong><br><em>Note:</em> This setting changes the behavior for obtaining the two-factor authentication code from using the password field to showing a separate prompt. If your theme overrides the default login page, you may not be able to use this option.'=>'<strong>启用双重身份验证代码的单独提示<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="wfhelp wf-inline-help"><span class="screen-reader-text">（在新标签页打开）</span></a></strong><br><em>注意：</em>此设置将获取双重身份验证代码的行为从使用密码字段更改为显示单独提示。如果您的主题覆盖了默认登录页面，您可能无法使用此选项。','<strong>Require Cellphone Sign-in for all Administrators<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="wfhelp wf-inline-help"><span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a></strong><br><em>Note:</em> This setting requires at least one administrator to have Cellphone Sign-in enabled. On multisite, this option applies only to super admins.'=>'<strong>要求所有管理员使用手机登录<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="wfhelp wf-inline-help"><span class="screen-reader-text">（在新标签页打开）</span></a></strong><br><em>注意：</em>此设置要求至少一名管理员启用手机登录。在多站点上，此选项仅适用于超级管理员。','Two-Factor Authentication Options'=>'双重身份认证选项','Display Live Traffic menu option'=>'显示实时流量菜单选项','Maximum days to keep Live Traffic data (1-30 days)'=>'保持实时流量数据的最长天数（最小值：1）','All Traffic'=>'所有流量','Security Only'=>'仅限安全','Traffic logging mode'=>'流量记录模式','Are you sure you want to restore the default Live Traffic settings? This will undo any custom changes you have made to the options on this page.'=>'您确定要恢复默认的实时流量设置吗？ 这将撤消您对此页面上的选项所做的任何自定义更改。','These options let you choose which traffic to log and to ignore certain types of visitors, based on their level of access, usernames, IP address, or browser type. If you run a high-traffic website where it is not feasible to see your visitors in real-time, simply change the <strong>Traffic logging mode</strong> to "Security Only."'=>'通过这些选项，您可以根据访问级别，用户名，IP 地址或浏览器类型选择要记录的流量并忽略某些类型的访问者。 如果您运营的流量较高的网站无法实时查看访问者，只需将<strong>流量记录模式</strong>更改为 “仅限安全”。','Live Traffic Options'=>'实时流量选项','Block<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Visitors Matching this</span> Pattern'=>'屏蔽<span class="wf-hidden-xs">符合该匹配</span>模式的访问者','Enter a reason'=>'输入一个原因','<span class="wf-hidden-xs">Block </span>Reason'=>'<span class="wf-hidden-xs">被拦截屏蔽</span>的原因','e.g., *badwebsite.example.com*'=>'举例来说, *badwebsite.example.com*','e.g., *badRobot*, *MSIE*, or *browserSuffix'=>'举例来说, *badRobot*, *MSIE*, 或者 *browserSuffix','<span class="wf-hidden-xs">Browser </span>User Agent'=>'<span class="wf-hidden-xs">浏览器</span>用户代理（User Agent）','e.g., *.amazonaws.com or *.linode.com'=>'举例来说, *.amazonaws.com or *.linode.com','e.g., 192.168.200.200 - 192.168.200.220 or 192.168.200.0/24'=>'举例来说：192.168.200.200 - 192.168.200.220 or 192.168.200.0/24','IP<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Address</span> Range'=>'IP <span class="wf-hidden-xs">地址范围</span>','Enter an IP address'=>'输入 IP 地址','IP<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Address to Block</span>'=>'IP <span class="wf-hidden-xs">地址加入黑名单</span>','Pick<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> from List</span>'=>'选择<span class="wf-hidden-xs">列表中</span>','Countries<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> to Block</span>'=>'国家 / 地区<span class="wf-hidden-xs">加入到黑名单</span>','<span class="wf-hidden-xs">Block access to the rest of the site</span><span class="wf-visible-xs">Rest of site</span>'=>'<span class="wf-hidden-xs">拦截访问网站的其余部分</span><span class="wf-visible-xs">其他网站</span>','Login Form'=>'登录表单','<span class="wf-hidden-xs">What to </span>Block'=>'<span class="wf-hidden-xs">加入什么到 </span>黑名单','Enter a duration (default is forever)'=>'输入持续时间（默认为永久）','Block Duration'=>'屏蔽时长','Country Blocking'=>'国家 / 地区拦截','<span class="wf-hidden-xs">Custom </span>Pattern'=>'<span class="wf-hidden-xs">自定义</span>模式','Block<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Visitors Matching this Pattern</span>'=>'屏蔽<span class="wf-hidden-xs">匹配此模式的访客</span>','Country'=>'国家 / 地区','Update<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Block</span>'=>'更新<span class="wf-hidden-xs">拦截屏蔽规则</span>','Block<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> the Selected Countries</span>'=>'屏蔽<span class="wf-hidden-xs">这些被选中的国家</span>','IP<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Address</span>'=>'IP <span class="wf-hidden-xs">地址</span>','Block<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> this IP Address</span>'=>'屏蔽<span class="wf-hidden-xs">这个 IP 地址</span>','Wordfence country blocking is designed to stop an attack, prevent content theft, or end malicious activity that originates from a geographic region in less than 1/300,000th of a second. Blocking countries who are regularly creating failed logins, a large number of page not found errors, and are clearly engaged in malicious activity is an effective way to protect your site during an attack.'=>'Wordfence 国家拦截被设计用来阻止攻击，防止内容盗窃，或者在不到 30 万分之一秒的时间内结束来自某个地理区域的恶意活动。封锁那些经常创建失败登录、大量页面未找到错误、且明显从事恶意活动的国家，是在攻击期间保护您的站点的有效方法。','Put Geographic Protection In Place With Country Blocking'=>'在适当位置作为地理保护以屏蔽国家 / 地区','Enter a full URL (e.g., http://example.com/blocked/)'=>'输入完整的网址（例如 http://example.com/blocked/）','URL to redirect blocked users to'=>'将被屏蔽的用户 URL 重定向到的','What to do when we block someone'=>'当我们屏蔽某人时该怎么办','Advanced Country Blocking Options'=>'国家 / 地区高级屏蔽选项','Are you sure you want to stop blocking the ${count} selected IPs, ranges, and countries?'=>'您确定要停止屏蔽 ${count}所选的 IP，范围和国家 / 地区吗？','Are you sure you want to stop blocking the selected IP, range, or country?'=>'您确定要停止屏蔽所选的 IP，范围或国家 / 地区吗？','Unblocking'=>'解除封锁中','Change Filter'=>'修改过滤','Clear Filter'=>'清空过滤条件','No blocks match the current filter.'=>'当前过滤器没有可匹配到屏蔽信息。','No blocks are currently active.'=>'目前没有任何被拦截的信息。','Last Attempt'=>'最后一次尝试','Block Count'=>'屏蔽计数','Expiration'=>'有效期','Reason'=>'原因','Rule Added'=>'规则被添加的时间','Detail'=>'详情','Block Type'=>'屏蔽类型','Export<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> All IPs</span>'=>'导出<span class="wf-hidden-xs">所有 IP </span>','Make Permanent'=>'手动永久屏蔽','Unblock'=>'取消屏蔽','Filter'=>'过滤','Filter by Type, Detail, or Reason'=>'按类型，详细信息或原因筛选','Show<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Wordfence</span> Automatic<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Blocks</span>'=>'显示<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> Wordfence</span> 自动<span class="wf-hidden-xs">屏蔽</span>','Current blocks<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> for %s</span>'=>'当前被 <span class="wf-hidden-xs">%s</span> 屏蔽的黑名单','Save'=>'保存','Back'=>'返回','Unblock All'=>'解锁全部','Block All'=>'屏蔽全部','Select Countries to Block from List'=>'选择要屏蔽的国家 / 地区列表','then set a cookie that will bypass country blocking in future in case that user hits the site from a blocked country.'=>'然后设置一个 cookie，如果用户从被阻止的国家 / 地区访问该网站，将来会绕过国家阻止。','/set-country-bypass/'=>'/set-country-bypass/','If user who is allowed to access the site views the relative URL'=>'如果允许访问该站点的用户查看相对 URL','Bypass Cookie'=>'绕过 Cookie','Manage global blocking options.'=>'管理全局屏蔽选项。','and set a cookie that will bypass all country blocking.'=>'并设置一个将绕过所有国家阻止的 cookie。','/page-name/'=>'/page-name/','then redirect that user to'=>'然后将该用户重定向到','/bypassurl/'=>'/bypassurl/','If user hits the relative URL'=>'如果用户点击相对 URL','Bypass Redirect'=>'绕过重定向','Done'=>'完成','Wordfence now includes the option to enable Google reCaptcha v3 on your WordPress login and registration pages. This adds a powerful new layer of protection against password guessing and credential stuffing attacks from bots without slowing down real users.'=>'Wordfence 现在包括在您的 WordPress 登录和注册页面上启用 Google reCaptcha v3 的选项。这为您增加了一个强大的新保护层，以防止来自机器人的密码猜测和凭证填充攻击，同时又不会降低真实用户的速度。','New Login Page Captcha Feature'=>'新的登录页验证码功能','Two-factor authentication now has its own IP allowlist. If necessary, you can allow specific IP addresses or ranges to skip 2FA when logging in.'=>'双因素认证现在有自己的 IP 白名单。如有必要，您可以允许特定的 IP 地址或范围在登录时跳过 2FA。','Individual Allowlisting'=>'个人白名单','We are excited to announce the release of a completely rebuilt two-factor authentication (2FA) feature within Wordfence. 2FA is an important layer of security that protects you from password guessing and credential stuffing attacks. Previously a Premium-only feature, it is now available for sites running the free version of Wordfence. You are now able to enable 2FA for any role, we’ve added a number of important security features, and we’ve significantly improved the admin interface.'=>'我们很高兴地宣布在 Wordfence 中发布了一个完全重建的双因素认证（2FA）功能。2FA 是一个重要的安全层，可以保护您免受密码猜测和凭证填充攻击。以前只有高级版才有此功能，现在它可用于运行免费版 Wordfence 的网站。您现在可以为任何角色启用 2FA，我们增加了许多重要的安全功能，并显著改善了管理界面。','Introducing the New Wordfence 2FA'=>'介绍新的 Wordfence 2FA 双重安全机制。','How do I get to 100%?'=>'如何达到 100%？','How does Wordfence determine this?'=>'Wordfence 如何确定这一点？','<strong>Congratulations!</strong> You\'ve optimized configurations for this feature! If you want to learn more about how this score is determined, click the link below.'=>'<strong>恭喜！！！</strong> 您已优化此功能的配置！ 如果您想了解有关如何确定此分数的更多信息，请单击下面的链接。','Please confirm the unsubscribe request for %s.'=>'请确认 %s 的取消订阅请求。','Please enter an email address to unsubscribe from alerts. If this email address exists on the alert email list, it will receive a confirmation link to unsubscribe.'=>'请输入电子邮件地址以取消订阅提醒。 如果此电子邮件地址存在于警报电子邮件列表中，它将收到取消订阅的确认链接。','If the email address provided was on the alert email list, it has been sent an unsubscribe link.'=>'如果提供的电子邮件地址位于警报电子邮件列表中，则会向其发送取消订阅链接。','The email address provided has been unsubscribed from future alert emails.'=>'已取消订阅警报电子邮件的电子邮件通知。','Confirm Unsubscribe'=>'确认取消订阅','Unsubscribe Successful'=>'取消订阅成功','Unsubscription Confirmation Sent'=>'已将确认取消订阅信息发送给您','Unsubscribe from Security Alerts'=>'取消订阅安全警报','Your computer\'s time: '=>'您的电脑时间：','Generated by Wordfence at '=>'由 Wordfence 生成 ','Please enter the license to install.'=>'请输入要安装的许可证。','The Wordfence license could not be installed.'=>'无法安装 Wordfence 许可证。','Return to the <a href="%s">Wordfence Admin Page</a>'=>'返回到 <a href="%s">Wordfence 管理控制面板</a>','The Wordfence license provided has been installed.'=>'Wordfence 许可证已安装。','Install Wordfence License'=>'安装 Wordfence 许可证','Wordfence License Installation Failed'=>'Wordfence 许可证安装失败','Wordfence License Installation Successful'=>'Wordfence 许可证安装成功','User defined scan pattern'=>'用户定义的扫描模式','Enable scan option to check if your website is on a domain blocklist.'=>'启用扫描选项以检查您的网站是否在域名黑名单中。','Enable scan option to check if your website IP is generating spam.'=>'启用扫描选项以检查您的网站 IP 是否正在生成垃圾邮件。','Enable scan option to check if this website is being "Spamvertised".'=>'启用扫描选项以检查此网站是否「被 Spamvertised」。','Enable Premium Reputation Checks.'=>'启用高级信誉检查。','Standard detection capability'=>'标准检测能力','Custom scan options selected'=>'选择自定义扫描选项','Standard detection capability, chance of false positives'=>'标准检测能力，有产生误报的可能性','Low resource utilization, limited detection capability'=>'资源利用率低，检测能力有限','Standard'=>'标准','Custom'=>'自定义','High Sensitivity'=>'高灵敏度','Limited'=>'限定','Quick'=>'快速','No block parameters provided.'=>'没有提供块参数。','Invalid hostname.'=>'主机名无效。','Invalid IP range.'=>'无效的 IP 范围。','Ranges mixing IPv4 and IPv6 addresses are not supported.'=>'不支持混合 IPv4 和 IPv6 地址的范围。','An invalid country was selected.'=>'选择了无效的国家 / 地区。','No countries selected.'=>'没有选择国家。','Nothing selected to block.'=>'没有选择阻止。','This IP address is in a range of addresses that Wordfence does not block. The IP range may be internal or belong to a service that is always allowed. Allowlisting of external services can be disabled. <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Learn More<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>'=>'此 IP 地址位于 Wordfence 不会阻止的地址范围内。该 IP 范围可能是内部的，也可能属于始终允许的服务。可以禁用外部服务的允许列表。<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">了解更多<span class="screen-reader-text">（在新标签页打开）</span></a>','Invalid IP address.'=>'无效的 IP 地址。','A block reason must be provided.'=>'必须提供拦截原因.','Invalid block duration.'=>'无效块持续时间。','Invalid block type.'=>'屏蔽类型无效。','Advanced Block'=>'高级屏蔽','Country Block'=>'国家屏蔽','Lockout'=>'锁定','IP Throttled'=>'IP 限制','IP Block'=>'IP 屏蔽','Support'=>'支持','Dashboard'=>'仪表盘','Enable Brute Force Protection.'=>'启用强力保护。','Disable Author Scanning.'=>'禁用作者扫描。','Enable Block Admin Registration.'=>'启用阻止管理员注册。','Enable Mask Login Errors.'=>'启用掩码登录错误。','Enforce Strong Passwords.'=>'强制使用强密码。','Enable Real-Time Wordfence Security Network.'=>'启用实时 Wordfence 安全网络。','Enable Real-Time IP Blocklist.'=>'启用实时 IP 黑名单。','Enable Firewall.'=>'启用防火墙。','Repair the Wordfence Firewall configuration.'=>'修复 Wordfence 防火墙配置。','Enable Rate Limiting and Advanced Blocking.'=>'启用速率限制和高级屏蔽。','Optimize the Wordfence Firewall.'=>'优化 Wordfence 防火墙。','Enable Premium Rules.'=>'启用高级规则。','Enable firewall.'=>'启用防火墙。','Basic Protection'=>'基本保护','Extended Protection'=>'扩展保护','Learning Mode'=>'学习模式','Skip'=>'跳过','Reminder: If you lose access to your authenticator device, you can use recovery codes to log in. If you have not saved a copy of your recovery codes, we recommend downloading them now.'=>'提醒如果您失去了对认证器设备的访问权限，您可以使用恢复码进行登录。如果您还没有保存恢复码的副本，我们建议您现在下载。','An error was encountered while trying to activate two-factor authentication. Please try again.'=>'在尝试激活双因素认证时遇到错误。请再试一次。','Error Activating 2FA'=>'激活双重安全机制出错','For help on setting up an app, visit our help article.'=>'有关设置应用程序的帮助，请访问我们的帮助文章。','Enter the code from your authenticator app below to verify and activate two-factor authentication for this account.'=>'在下面的验证器应用中输入代码，验证并激活该账户的双因素验证。','Optional'=>'选项','Download Recovery Codes'=>'下载恢复代码','2. Enter Code from Authenticator App'=>'2 、从认证器应用程序中输入代码','An error was encountered while trying to deactivate two-factor authentication. Please try again.'=>'在尝试停用双因素认证时遇到错误。请再试一次。','Error Deactivating 2FA'=>'停用 2FA时出错','Are you sure you want to deactivate two-factor authentication?'=>'您确定要停用双因素认证吗？','Deactivate 2FA'=>'停用 2FA','Deactivate'=>'禁用','Wordfence two-factor authentication is currently active on the account <strong>%s</strong>. You may deactivate it by clicking the button below.'=>'帐户上的 Wordfence 双因素认证目前处于激活状态。 <strong>%s</strong>.您可以通过点击下面的按钮将其停用。','Wordfence two-factor authentication is currently active on your account. You may deactivate it by clicking the button below.'=>'Wordfence 双因素认证目前在您的账户上处于激活状态。您可以通过点击下面的按钮来停用它。','Wordfence 2FA Active'=>'激活的 Wordfence 2FA','1. Scan Code or Enter Key'=>'1 、扫描码或输入 Key','An error was encountered while trying to generate new recovery codes. Please try again.'=>'在尝试生成新的恢复代码时遇到了错误。请再试一次。','New Recovery Codes'=>'新的恢复代码','Each line of %d letters and numbers is a single recovery code, with optional spaces for readability. To use a recovery code, after entering your username and password, enter the code like "1234 5678 90AB CDEF" at the 2FA prompt. If your site has a custom login prompt and does not show a 2FA prompt, you can use the single-step method by entering your password and the code together in the Password field, like "mypassword1234 5678 90AB CDEF". Your recovery codes are:'=>'每一行%d 字母和数字都是一个恢复码，为了便于阅读，可以选择空格。使用恢复码时，在输入用户名和密码后，在 2FA 提示下输入「1234 5678 90AB CDEF」等代码。如果您的网站有自定义登录提示，没有显示 2FA 提示，您可以使用单步法，在密码栏里把密码和代码一起输入，比如「mypassword1234 5678 90AB CDEF」。您的恢复码是','Two-Factor Authentication Recovery Codes - %s (%s)'=>'双因素认证恢复码-%s (%s)','Use one of these %d codes to log in if you lose access to your authenticator device. Codes are %d characters long plus optional spaces. Each one may be used only once.'=>'如果您失去了对身份验证器设备的访问权限，请使用这些%d 代码之一进行登录。代码长度为%d 个字符，外加可选的空格。每个代码只能使用一次。','Error Generating New Codes'=>'新代码生成错误','Generate'=>'生成','Are you sure you want to generate new recovery codes? Any remaining unused codes will be disabled.'=>'您确定要生成新的恢复代码吗？任何剩余的未使用的代码将被禁用。','Generate New Recovery Codes'=>'生成新的恢复代码','Generate New Codes'=>'生成新代码','Recovery Codes'=>'恢复代码','If enabled, all settings and 2FA records will be deleted on deactivation. If later reactivated, all users that previously had 2FA active will need to set it up again.'=>'如果启用，所有设置和双重安全机制记录将在停用时删除。如果稍后重新激活，以前处于活动状态的所有用户都需要重新设置它。','Delete Login Security tables and data on deactivation'=>'停用后删除登录安全性的表和数据','While in test mode, reCAPTCHA will score login and registration requests but not actually block them. The scores will be recorded and can be used to select a human/bot threshold value.'=>'在测试模式下，reCAPTCHA 将对登录和注册请求进行评分，但不会实际阻止它们。分数将被记录下来，并可用于选择一个人类 / 机器人的阈值。','Run reCAPTCHA in test mode'=>'在测试模式下运行 reCAPTCHA','Allowlisted IPs must be placed on separate lines. You can specify ranges using the following formats: 127.0.0.1/24, 127.0.0.[1-100], or 127.0.0.1-127.0.1.100.'=>'白名单的 IP 必须放在不同的行上。您可以使用以下格式指定范围。 127.0.0.1/24 、 127.0.0.[1-100] 或 127.0.0.1-127.0.1.100。','Disable XML-RPC authentication'=>'禁用 XML-RPC 身份验证','Required'=>'必填','Skipped'=>'跳过','If enabled, XML-RPC calls that require authentication will also require a valid 2FA code to be appended to the password. You must choose the "Skipped" option if you use the WordPress app, the Jetpack plugin, or other services that require XML-RPC.'=>'如果启用，需要身份验证的 XML-RPC 调用还需要将有效的双重安全机制代码追加到密码中。如果您使用 WordPress 应用、 Jetpack 插件或其他需要 XML-RPC 的服务，则必须选择「跳过」选项。','Require 2FA for XML-RPC call authentication'=>'XML-RPC 调用身份验证需要双重安全机制','If enabled, users with 2FA enabled may choose to be prompted for a code only once every 30 days per device.'=>'如果启用，启用双重安全机制的用户可以选择每 30 天仅提示用户一次代码。','Allow remembering device for 30 days'=>'允许设备保留 30 天记忆','Super Administrator'=>'超级管理员','Save<span class="wfls-visible-sm-inline"> Changes</span>'=>'保存<span class="wfls-visible-sm-inline">更改</span>','Cancel<span class="wfls-visible-sm-inline"> Changes</span>'=>'取消<span class="wfls-visible-sm-inline">更改</span>','* User counts currently only reflect the main site on multisite installations.'=>'* 用户计数目前仅反映多站点安装的主站点。','Total Users'=>'用户总数','Role'=>'角色','Manage Users'=>'管理用户','User Summary'=>'用户摘要','Detected IP:'=>'检测到的 IP：','Corrected Time (WF):'=>'纠正时间 (WF):','Corrected Time (NTP):'=>'纠正时间（NTP）：','Browser Time:'=>'浏览器时间：','Server Time:'=>'服务器时间：','(you)'=>'(您)','Editing User:&nbsp;&nbsp;%s <span class="wfls-text-plain">%s</span>'=>'编辑用户。 %s <span class="wfls-text-plain">%s</span>','Two-Factor Authentication, or 2FA, significantly improves login security for your website. Wordfence 2FA works with a number of TOTP-based apps like Google Authenticator, FreeOTP, and Authy. For a full list of tested TOTP-based apps, <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">click here</a>.'=>'双因素认证，或 2FA，显著提高了您网站的登录安全性。Wordfence 2FA 可与许多基于 TOTP 的应用程序配合使用，如 Google Authenticator 、 FreeOTP 和 Authy。有关基于 TOTP 的测试应用程序的完整列表，请<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">点击这里</a>。','The request was flagged as suspicious, and we need verification that you attempted to log in to allow it to proceed. This verification link <b>will be valid for 15 minutes</b> from the time it was sent. If you did not attempt this login, please change your password immediately.'=>'该请求被标记为可疑，我们需要验证您是否尝试登录以允许其继续。此验证链接的<b>有效期为发送后 15分钟</b>。如果您没有尝试此次登录，请立即更改密码。','IP:'=>'IP：','Request Time:'=>'请求时间：','Count'=>'数量','reCAPTCHA Score History'=>'reCAPTCHA 的得分历史','Requests'=>'请求','Reset Score Statistics'=>'重置分数统计','A reCAPTCHA score equal to or higher than this value will be considered human. Anything lower will be treated as a bot and require additional verification for login and registration.'=>'等于或高于该值的 reCAPTCHA分数将被视为人类。 较低的任何内容都将被视为漫游器，并且需要其他验证才能登录和注册。','reCAPTCHA human/bot threshold score'=>'reCAPTCHA 人 / 机器人阈值分数','0.2'=>'0.2','0.3'=>'0.3','0.4'=>'0.4','0.5 (probably a human)'=>'0.5 （可能是人类）','0.6'=>'0.6','0.7'=>'0.7','0.8'=>'0.8','0.9'=>'0.9','1.0 (definitely a human)'=>'1.0 （绝对是人类）','reCAPTCHA v3 Secret'=>'reCAPTCHA v3 Secret','reCAPTCHA v3 Site Key'=>'reCAPTCHA v3 站点密钥','reCAPTCHA v3 does not make users solve puzzles or click a checkbox like previous versions. The only visible part is the reCAPTCHA logo. If a visitor\'s browser fails the CAPTCHA, Wordfence will send an email to the user\'s address with a link they can click to verify that they are a user of your site. You can read further details <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">in our documentation</a>.'=>'reCAPTCHA v3 并不像以前的版本那样让用户解开谜题或点击复选框。唯一可见的部分是 reCAPTCHA 标志。如果访问者的浏览器未能通过验证码，Wordfence 将向用户的地址发送一封电子邮件，其中包含一个链接，用户可以点击该链接来验证他们是否是您网站的用户。您可以<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">在我们的文档中</a>阅读更多细节。','Enable reCAPTCHA on the login and user registration pages'=>'在登录和用户注册页面上启用 reCAPTCHA','These IPs (or CIDR ranges) will be ignored when determining the requesting IP via the X-Forwarded-For HTTP header. Enter one IP or CIDR range per line.'=>'通过 X-Forwarded-For HTTP 标头确定请求 IP时，将忽略这些 IP（或 CIDR 范围）。 每行输入一个 IP 或 CIDR 范围。','How to get IPs'=>'如何获得 IP','Use the X-Real-IP HTTP header. Only use if you have a front-end proxy or spoofing may result.'=>'使用 X-Real-IP HTTP 标头。 仅在您拥有前端代理时才使用，否则可能会导致欺骗。','Use the X-Forwarded-For HTTP header. Only use if you have a front-end proxy or spoofing may result.'=>'使用 X-Forwarded-For HTTP 标头。 仅在您拥有前端代理时才使用，否则可能会导致欺骗。','Use PHP\'s built in REMOTE_ADDR and don\'t use anything else. Very secure if this is compatible with your site.'=>'使用 PHP 内置的 REMOTE_ADDR，不要使用其他任何东西。 如果这与您的网站兼容，则非常安全。','(Recommended)'=>'（推荐）','Use the most secure method to get visitor IP addresses. Prevents spoofing and works with most sites.'=>'使用最安全的方法获取访问者 IP 地址。防止欺骗，适用于大多数网站。','Premium Feature'=>'高级功能','An error was encountered while trying to send the notification. Please try again.'=>'在尝试发送通知时遇到了错误。请再试一次。','Notification Sent'=>'已发送通知','Error Sending Notification'=>'错误发送通知','If you\'re looking for a more comprehensive solution, the <a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">full Wordfence plugin</a> includes all of the features in this plugin as well as a full-featured WordPress firewall, a security scanner, live traffic, and more. The standard installation includes a robust set of free features that can be upgraded via a Premium license key.'=>'如果您正在寻找一个更全面的解决方案，<a href="%s" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">完整的 Wordfence 插件</a>包括这个插件中的所有功能，以及一个全功能的 WordPress 防火墙，一个安全扫描仪，实时流量等。标准安装包括一套强大的免费功能，可以通过高级许可密钥进行升级。','You have just installed the Wordfence Login Security plugin. It contains a subset of the functionality found in the full Wordfence plugin: Two-factor Authentication, XML-RPC Protection and Login Page CAPTCHA.'=>'您刚刚安装了 Wordfence 登录安全插件。它包含了完整的 Wordfence 插件中的部分功能。双因素验证、 XML-RPC 保护和登录页面验证码。','Wordfence Login Security Installed'=>'安装了 Wordfence 登录安全','<a class="wfls-btn wfls-btn-default wfls-btn-sm wfls-dismiss-link" href="#" onclick="GWFLS.dismiss_notice(\'%s\'); return false;">Dismiss</a>'=>'<a class="wfls-btn wfls-btn-default wfls-btn-sm wfls-dismiss-link" href="#" onclick="GWFLS.dismiss_notice(\'%s\'); return false;">放弃</a>','Learn more<span class="wfls-hidden-xs"> about Login Security</span>'=>'了解更多<span class="wfls-hidden-xs"> 关于登录安全的信息</span>','Login Security Settings'=>'登录安全设置','Settings'=>'设置','Learn more<span class="wfls-hidden-xs"> about Two-Factor Authentication</span>'=>'了解更多<span class="wfls-hidden-xs"> 关于双因素认证的信息</span>','Login Security'=>'登录安全性：为这些角色启用双重安全机制','Email verification invalid or expired. Please try again.'=>'电子邮件验证无效或过期。请重试。','Email verification succeeded. Please continue logging in.'=>'电子邮件验证成功。请继续登录。','<strong>REGISTRATION BLOCKED</strong>: The registration request was blocked because it was flagged as spam. Please try again or contact the site owner for help.'=>'<strong>注册被阻止</strong>：注册请求被阻止，因为它被标记为垃圾邮件。请再试一次或联系网站所有者寻求帮助。','<strong>REGISTRATION BLOCKED</strong>: The registration request was blocked because it was flagged as spam. Please try again or <a href="#" class="wfls-registration-captcha-contact" data-token="%s">contact the site owner</a> for help.'=>'<strong>注册被阻止</strong>：注册请求被阻止，因为它被标记为垃圾邮件。请再试一次或<a href="#" class="wfls-registration-captcha-contact" data-token="%s">联系网站所有者</a>寻求帮助。','<strong>REGISTRATION ATTEMPT BLOCKED</strong>: The security token for the login attempt was invalid or expired. Please reload the page and try again.'=>'<strong>注册尝试被阻止</strong>：登录尝试的安全令牌无效或过期。请重新加载页面并再次尝试。','<strong>REGISTRATION ATTEMPT BLOCKED</strong>: This site requires a security token created when the page loads for all registration attempts. Please ensure JavaScript is enabled and try again.'=>'<strong>注册尝试被阻止</strong>：本网站需要在页面加载时为所有注册尝试创建一个安全令牌。请确保 JavaScript 已启用，并再次尝试。','You do not currently have two-factor authentication active on your account, which will be required beginning %s. <a href="%s">Configure 2FA</a>'=>'您的账户上目前没有激活双因素身份验证，从 %s 开始，您需要激活双因素身份验证。<a href="%s">配置 2FA</a>','<strong>CODE REQUIRED</strong>: Please provide your 2FA code when prompted.'=>'<strong>代码要求</strong>。请在提示时提供您的 2FA 代码。','<strong>CODE REQUIRED</strong>: Please enter your 2FA code immediately after your password in the same field.'=>'<strong>代码要求</strong>。请在密码后的同一栏目中输入您的 2FA 代码。','<strong>CODE INVALID</strong>: The 2FA code provided is either expired or invalid. Please try again.'=>'<strong>代码无效</strong>：所提供的 2FA 代码过期或无效。请重试。','Login Verification Required'=>'登录验证要求','Manage 2FA Settings'=>'管理 2FA 设置','Two-factor authentication is not currently enabled for this account type. To enable it, visit the Wordfence 2FA Settings page.'=>'目前尚未为该账户类型启用双因素验证。要启用它，请访问 Wordfence 2FA 设置页面。','Activate 2FA'=>'激活双重安全机制','Manage 2FA'=>'管理双重安全机制','Wordfence 2FA is inactive.'=>'Wordfence 双重安全机制未启用。','Wordfence 2FA is active.'=>'Wordfence 双重安全机制启用。','Wordfence Login Security'=>'Wordfence 登录安全性','reCAPTCHA test mode is enabled. While enabled, login and registration requests will be checked for their score but will not be blocked if the score is below the minimum score. <a href="%s">Manage Settings</a>'=>'启用了 reCAPTCHA 测试模式。启用后，登录和注册请求将被检查其分数，但如果分数低于最低分数，则不会被阻止。<a href="%s">管理设置</a>','XML-RPC authentication is disabled. Jetpack is currently active and requires XML-RPC authentication to work correctly. <a href="%s">Manage Settings</a>'=>'XML-RPC 认证被禁用。Jetpack 目前处于活动状态，需要 XML-RPC 认证才能正常工作。<a href="%s">管理设置</a>','Login Security options are available on the Login Security options page'=>'登录安全选项可在登录安全选项页面上找到','Login Security Options'=>'更新登录安全选项','Login Security: Enable reCAPTCHA on the login and user registration pages'=>'登录安全。在登录和用户注册页面启用重新验证码','Login Security: Disable XML-RPC authentication'=>'登录安全。禁用 XML-RPC 认证','Login Security: Require 2FA for XML-RPC call authentication'=>'登录安全性：XML-RPC 调用身份验证需要双重安全机制','Login Security: Allow remembering device for 30 days'=>'登录安全性：允许设备保留 30 天记忆','Login Security: Enable 2FA for these roles'=>'登录安全性：为这些角色启用双重安全机制','An error was encountered while validating the reCAPTCHA site key: %s'=>'在验证 reCAPTCHA 站点密钥时遇到一个错误：%s','Unable to validate the reCAPTCHA site key. Please check the key and try again.'=>'无法验证 reCAPTCHA 网站密钥。请检查密钥并再次尝试。','An invalid IP source was provided.'=>'提供了一个无效的 IP 源。','The IP/range %s is invalid.'=>'IP/ 范围 %s 无效。','A reminder to activate two-factor authentication was sent to %d user.'=>'向 %d 管理员发送了激活双因素认证的提醒。','A reminder to activate two-factor authentication was sent to %d users.'=>'向 %d 管理员发送了激活双因素认证的提醒。','2FA will soon be required on %s'=>'%s 即将要求使用 2FA','You do not have permission to generate new recovery codes.'=>'您没有权限生成新的恢复代码。','You do not have permission to generate new recovery codes for the given user.'=>'您没有权限为指定用户生成新的恢复代码。','The user specified does not have two-factor authentication active.'=>'指定的用户没有激活双因素认证。','You do not have permission to deactivate 2FA.'=>'您没有权限停用 2FA。','The user does not exist.'=>'用户不存在。','You do not have permission to deactivate the given user.'=>'您没有权限停用指定的用户。','%d unused recovery codes remain. You may generate a new set by clicking below.'=>'剩余 %d 个未使用的恢复代码。您可以通过点击下面的按钮生成一组新的恢复代码。','%d unused recovery code remains. You may generate a new set by clicking below.'=>'剩余 %d 未使用的恢复代码。您可以通过点击下面的按钮生成一组新的恢复代码。','The code provided does not match the expected value. Please verify that the time on your authenticator device is correct and that this server\'s time is correct.'=>'提供的代码与预期值不符。请验证您的验证器设备上的时间是否正确，以及此服务器的时间是否正确。','The given user already has two-factor authentication active.'=>'给定的用户已经激活了双因素认证。','You do not have permission to activate 2FA.'=>'您没有激活 2FA 的权限。','The given user does not exist.'=>'给定的用户不存在。','You do not have permission to activate the given user.'=>'您没有权限激活指定的用户。','<strong>ERROR</strong>: An error occurred while sending the message. Please try again.'=>'<strong>错误</strong>：发送信息时发生错误。发送信息时发生了错误。请重试。','<strong>MESSAGE SENT</strong>: Your message was sent to the site owner.'=>'<strong>已发送</strong>：消息。您的信息已发送给网站所有者。','A visitor blocked from registration sent the following message.

