请求类型（人类与爬虫）的速率限制可能不太准确，因为这可以防止加载用于该标识的额外 JavaScript。','Greetings! The default configuration for Wordfence Live Traffic has changed. The new default saves only logins and blocked requests, while this site is currently recording all traffic. Would you like to change to the new default?'=>'您好！ Wordfence 实时流量的默认配置已更改。 新的默认设置仅保存登录和被阻止的请求，而此站点当前正在记录所有流量。 您想更改为新的默认值吗？','Recommended Settings Change'=>'推荐设置更改','The main navigation no longer includes an <strong>Options</strong> link. Options are now accessed via the <strong>Options</strong> link on each feature\'s main page. Live Traffic is now located in the Tools section, and blocking is found under the Firewall. Shortcuts to add a <strong>Blocking</strong> link back to the main navigation are available under Blocking options.'=>'主导航不再包含<strong>选项</strong>链接。 现在可以通过每个功能主页上的<strong>选项</strong>链接访问选项。 实时流量现在位于「工具」部分，并且可以在防火墙下找到阻止。 阻止选项下提供了将<strong>阻止</strong>链接添加回主导航的快捷方式。','Updated Navigation'=>'更新导航','Manage your Wordfence license, see alerts and automatic plugin updates, and import/export your settings.'=>'管理您的 Wordfence 许可证，查看警报和自动插件更新，以及导入 / 导出您的设置。','Each feature contains a status percentage reminding you at a high level of what\'s enabled, disabled, or needing your attention. The Notifications section highlights actions you need to take.'=>'每个功能都包含一个状态百分比，提醒您高级别启用，禁用或需要您注意的内容。 通知部分突出显示您需要采取的操作。','Monitor Your Wordfence Protection'=>'监控您的 Wordfence 保护','We welcome your feedback and comments at <a href="mailto:feedback@wordfence.com">feedback@wordfence.com</a>. For a deeper dive on all of the changes, <a href="https://www.wordfence.com/blog/2018/01/introducing-wordfence-7/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">click here<span class="screen-reader-text"> (opens in new tab)</span></a>.'=>'欢迎您通过 <a href="mailto:feedback@wordfence.com">feedback@wordfence.com</a> 提供反馈和评论。如需深入了解所有更改，请<a href="https://www.wordfence.com/blog/2018/01/introducing-wordfence-7/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">点击此处<span class="screen-reader-text">（在新标签页打开）</span></a>。','This update includes a number of significant interface changes. We\'d like to walk you through  some of them, but you can bypass the tour for a section at any time by closing the dialogs.'=>'此更新包括许多重要的界面更改。 我们想引导您完成其中的一些内容，但是您可以通过关闭对话框随时绕过巡视。','You have successfully updated to Wordfence %s'=>'您已成功更新至 Wordfence %s','You\'ll find this icon throughout the plugin. Clicking it will show you the options and features for each section of Wordfence. From the dashboard, you can find the <strong>Global Options</strong> for Wordfence such as alerts, automatic updates, and managing your site\'s Premium License.'=>'您会在整个插件中找到这个图标。 单击它将显示 Wordfence 的每个部分的选项和功能。 在仪表板中，您可以找到 Wordfence 的<strong>全局选项</strong>，例如警报，自动更新和管理站点的高级许可证。','Global Wordfence Options'=>'全局 Wordfence 选项','Each feature contains a status that reminds you what\'s enabled, disabled or needs attention. The Notifications section will highlight actions you need to take.'=>'每个功能都包含一个状态，提醒您启用，禁用或需要注意的内容。 通知部分将突出显示您需要采取的操作。','Easily Monitor Your Wordfence Protection'=>'轻松监控您的 Wordfence 保护','The Wordfence Dashboard provides valuable insights into the current state of your site\'s security. You\'ll find useful data summarized here as well as important status updates and notifications.'=>'Wordfence 仪表板提供有关站点安全性当前状态的宝贵见解。 您将在此处找到有用的数据以及重要的状态更新和通知。','This is your Dashboard'=>'这是您的控制面板','Manage global options for Wordfence such as alerts, premium status, and more'=>'管理 Wordfence 的全局选项，例如警报，高级状态等','Global Options'=>'全局选项','Live Traffic, Whois Lookup, Import/Export, and Diagnostics'=>'实时流量、 Whois 查询、导入 / 导出和诊断','Tools'=>'工具','Learn more<span class="wf-hidden-xs"> about the Dashboard</span>'=>'了解详情<span class="wf-hidden-xs">关于控制面板</span>','Wordfence Dashboard'=>'Wordfence 控制面板','To clone one site\'s configuration to another, use the import/export tools below.'=>'要将一个站点的配置克隆到另一个站点，请使用下面的导入 / 导出工具。','Connect Site'=>'连接网站','To connect your site your site to Wordfence Central, use the link below:'=