le and Bing.'=>'Wordfence 实时流量会实时显示您网站上发生的情况，包括用户登录，黑客尝试以及 Wordfence 防火墙阻止的请求。 您可以选择仅记录与安全相关的流量或所有流量。 流量直接记录在服务器上，这意味着它包括不执行 JavaScript 的访问。 Google 和其他基于 JavaScript 的分析软件包通常仅显示由人工操作的浏览器的访问，而实时流量可以显示来自 Google 和 Bing 等爬虫的访问。','Click inside window to resume'=>'单击窗口内部以恢复','Live Updates Paused'=>'暂停实时更新','Live Traffic'=>'实时流量','Continue'=>'继续','Congratulations! Wordfence Premium is now active on your website. Please note that some Premium features are not enabled by default.'=>'恭喜！ Wordfence Premium 现已在您的网站上有效。 请注意，默认情况下不启用某些高级功能。','Premium License Installed'=>'安装了高级许可证','View Documentation'=>'查看文档','Documentation about Wordfence may be found on our website by clicking the button below or by clicking the <i class="wf-fa wf-fa-question-circle-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> links on any of the plugin\'s pages.'=>'有关 Wordfence 的文档可以在我们的网站上找到，方法是单击下面的按钮或单击<i class="wf-fa wf-fa-question-circle-o" aria-hidden="true"> </i>链接任何插件的页面。','Documentation'=>'文档','Top Topics and Questions'=>'热门话题和问题','All Documentation'=>'所有文档','To continue using Defiant products and services including the Wordfence plugin, all customers must review and agree to the updated terms and privacy policies. These changes reflect our commitment to follow data protection best practices and regulations. The Wordfence interface will remain disabled until these terms are agreed to.'=>'要继续使用 Defiant 产品和服务（包括 Wordfence 插件），所有客户都必须查看并同意更新的条款和隐私政策。 这些变化反映了我们遵守数据保护最佳实践和法规的承诺。 在同意这些条款之前，Wordfence 接口将保持禁用状态。','Agreement to New Terms and Privacy Policies'=>'同意新条款和隐私政策','The GDPR is a set of rules that provides more control over EU personal data. Defiant has updated its terms of service, privacy policies, and software, as well as made available standard contractual clauses to meet GDPR compliance.'=>'GDPR 是一套规则，可以更好地控制欧盟个人数据。 Defiant 已更新其使用条款，隐私政策和软件，并提供数据处理协议以符合 GDPR 合规性。','General Data Protection Regulation'=>'通用数据保护条例','GDPR Information'=>'GDPR 信息','Upgrade Now to Access Premium Support'=>'立即升级以访问高级支持','Our senior support 